Ukwanda okusheshayo kokuqubuka kwesifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19) e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom, kusukela ngo-1 January kuya ku-15 March 2020
Ukuqubuka okuhlangene kwezifo ze-coronavirus (i-COVID-19) kukhombisa ukuthambekela okufanayo emazweni e-European Union/European Economic Area nase-United Kingdom okuqinisekisa ukuthi, nakuba kusesigabeni esihlukile kuye ngezwe, ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luqhubeka ngokushesha kuwo wonke amazwe.
Ngokusekelwe kulwazi olutholakale e-Italy, amazwe, izibhedlela kanye namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kufanele kwandise ukuzilungiselela kwabo ukwanda kweziguli ze-COVID-19 ezizodinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukunakekelwa okujulile.
Ngo-31 Disemba 2019, kwabikwa isiqephu sezigameko zesifo samaphaphu esingaziwa ukuthi sibangelwa yini eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Ngo-January 9, 2020, i-China Center for Disease Control and Prevention yabika ukuthi imbangela ingumdlavuza we-corona manje obizwa ngokuthi yi-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, isifo esibangelwa ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 sibizwa ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubufakazi kuze kube manje ukuthi cishe u-80% wabantu abane-COVID-19 banesifo esibuthakathaka, okusho ukuthi ukutheleleka komgudu wokuphefumula okuhambisana noma okungahambelani ne-pneumonia, futhi iningi labo liyaphila.
Ezimweni ezingaba ngu-14% i-COVID-19 iba yisifo esibi kakhulu esidinga ukufakwa esibhedlela kanti ezimweni ezisele ezingu-6% kuba nesifo esibucayi esidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile.
Izinga lokufa kweziguli ezilaliswe esibhedlela ngenxa ye-COVID-19 licishe libe ngu-4%.
Kulolu cwaningo, sihlola izinga lokwanda kwe-COVID-19 ezweni ngalinye le-European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) nase-United Kingdom (UK) bese siliqhathanisa nelesisifundazwe saseHubei, eChina.
Sibuye siqhathanise inani lamanje lamacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK nalelo lase-Italy phakathi kuka-31 Januwari-15 Mashi 2020.
Amacala e-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Ngemuva kweChina, i-COVID-19 yaqhubeka nokusabalala ngokwendawo futhi amandla obhubhane lwe-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke njengamanje alandela lawo alelizwe.
Ngo-11 Mashi 2020, uMqondisi Jikelele weNhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) wamemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyinhlupho.
Ekulandeni kuka-March 5 kwe-Eurosurveillance 2020, uSpiteri et al. wabika ngamacala okuqala e-Europe aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19 ngokwencazelo yamacala e-WHO.
E-EU/EEA, amacala amathathu okuqala aqinisekisiwe abikwa yiFrance ngo-24 January 2020 kubantu ababebuya eWuhan, esifundazweni saseHubei, eChina.
Ngo-15 Mashi 2020, amacala e-COVID-19 ayetholakale kuwo wonke amazwe angama-30 e-EU/EEA nase-United Kingdom (UK), lapho phakathi kuka-31 Disemba 2019 kanye nalolo suku, kwabikwa amacala angama-39,768 nokufa kwabantu abangu-1,727 kanti amacala angu-17,750 nokufa kwabantu abangu-1,441 kwavela e-Italy kuphela.
Ukuthola inani elihlangene kanye nokwenzeka okuhlangene kwamacala e-COVID-19
E-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC), inani lamacala e-COVID-19 abikiwe ezweni ngalinye emhlabeni jikelele, atholakala emithonjeni esemthethweni kuphela njenge-Ministry of Health, iziphathimandla zezempilo zikazwelonke nezifundazwe kanye ne-WHO, avuselelwa nsuku zonke ngo-8: 00 ekuseni.
Le mininingwane isetshenziselwe ukuhlola ukuthambekela kwe-COVID-19 e-EU/EEA nase-UK, nokuqhathanisa lokho ne-Italy.
Njengomfanekiso wokwanda kwamacala asebenzayo e-COVID-19, sibala inani eliqongelelweyo lezinsuku ezingu-14 lamacala e-COVID-19, ngaleyo ndlela kucatshangelwa inkambo yemvelo ye-COVID-19, ezweni ngalinye le-EU/EEA nase-UK, phakathi kuka-1 Januwari kuya ku-15 Mashi 2020.
Siphinde saveza inani elihlanganisiwe lamacala abikiwe ezweni ngalinye ngo-15 Mashi 2020 8:00 ekuseni uma kuqhathaniswa nelase-Italy esikhathini esiphakathi kuka-31 Januwari kuya ku-15 Mashi 2020.
Izindlela ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK
Amathrendi ezinsuku eziyi-14 ezenzakalelayo ezihlanganisiwe zezigameko ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK ngokuvamile alandela lawo esifundazweni sase-Hubei (eChina) (Umdwebo 1).
E-EU/EEA nase-UK jikelele, ukuqubuka okuhlanganisiwe kwe-COVID-19 kwaqala ukwanda cishe ngo-21 February bese kukhuphuka kakhulu cishe ngo-28 February 2020 (Izinto ezingeziwe).
Lokhu kwakubangelwa kakhulu ukwanda okusheshayo kwenani lamacala abikiwe e-Italy, kodwa wonke amanye amazwe e-EU/EEA kanye ne-UK babonisa izitayela ezifanayo zokwanda kwenani elihlangene le-COVID-19 (Izinto ezingeziwe).
Umdwebo 2 ukhombisa inani elihlanganisiwe lezigameko ze-COVID-19 emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK uma kuqhathaniswa nelase-Italy esikhathini esiphakathi kuka-31 Januwari kuya ku-15 Mashi 2020.
Igcizelela ukuthi, ngo-15 Mashi 8:00 ekuseni, amanye amazwe angu-15 e-EU/EEA ne-UK base bevele bebike inani eliphelele lamacala afana nalelo lase-Italy emasontweni amathathu ngaphambili noma ngaphansi.
Imiphumela yethu ibonisa ukuthi inani lamacala aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19 landa ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Amathrendi abonwe ezenzakalweni ezihlanganisiwe ze-COVID-19 asikisela ukuthi ubhadane luqhubeka ngesivinini esifanayo kuwo wonke amazwe.
Lokhu kwenzeka naphezu kokuba amazwe esemazingeni ahlukene, ukwehluka kwezimpendulo zikazwelonke zezempilo yomphakathi, futhi mhlawumbe nezincazelo ezahlukene zamacala emazweni kanye nezinqubo ezahlukene zokukhetha iziguli okumele zihlolwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe ukuthi zinalo i-COVID-19, kuhlanganise nokuhlolwa kokulandela.
Ekuqaleni kuka-March 2020, odokotela ezifundeni ezithintekile e-Italy bachaza isimo lapho cishe u-10% weziguli ezine-COVID-19 zidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile futhi imithombo yabezindaba ibike ukuthi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kulezi zifunda sebefinyelele amandla abo aphezulu.
Idatha yokungeniswa kweziguli ze-COVID-19 esibhedlela kanye/noma endaweni yokwelashwa okunzulu okwamanje iyatholakala ezingeni le-EU/EEA ngamacala angu-6% no-1% kuphela, ngokulandelana (idatha ayiboniswa).
Nokho, kufanele ziqoqwe ngendlela ehlelekile ukuze ziqede idatha yamanje yokuqapha egxile enanini lamacala abikiwe kanye nasenani labafayo.
Ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-201011 lubonise ukwehluka okukhulu ekutholakaleni kwemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile kanye nokunakekelwa okuphakathi eYurophu, kusuka ku-29,2 eJalimane kuya ku-4,2 emibhedeni ngabantu abangu-100 000 ePortugal.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi amazwe angase abe namathuluzi amaningi noma ambalwa kune-Italy (12.5 imibhede yokunakekelwa okunzulu nokunakekelwa okuphakathi ngabantu abangu-100 000 ngo-201011).
Izimo zokumodela ezihlobene nokugcwala kwamandla ezempilo, nezibalo zezwe ngalinye le-EU/EEA ne-UK zokubhebhetheka kwamacala e-COVID-19 asezibhedlela ahambisana ne-90% ingozi yokweqa amandla emibhede yokunakekelwa okunzulu, zinikezwe ekubuyekezweni kwesithupha kwe-ECDC okusheshayo kokulinganisela ingozi ye-COVID-19.
Njengoba amacala kuze kube manje eqoqwe ezindaweni ezithile emazweni e-EU/EEA nase-UK, futhi izibhedlela namayunithi okunakekelwa okujulile kuvame ukuhlinzeka abantu abanomthelela esifundeni, imininingwane mayelana namacala kanye nemibhede yokunakekelwa okujulile kufanele ifakwe ku-Nomenclature of Territorial Units for Statistics 2 (NUTS-2) level.
Okuhlangenwe nakho kwase-Italy kanye nokuthambekela kwamanje kwamanye amazwe kubonisa ukuthi ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luya phambili ngokushesha e-EU/EEA nase-UK.
Ngakho-ke amazwe, izibhedlela kanye namayunithi ezinhlelo zokunakekelwa okujulile kufanele bazilungiselele isimo sokudluliswa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 emphakathini okuqhubekayo kanye nokwanda kwenani leziguli ezine-COVID-19 ezidinga ukunakekelwa kwezempilo, futhi ikakhulukazi ukwelashwa okujulile, njengalokho okwenzeka ezifundeni ezithintekile e-Italy.
Njengoba kuphawulwe ekuhloleni okusheshayo kwe-ECDC kwakamuva, indlela esheshayo, ehlelekile nebanzi ibalulekile ukubambezela ukusakazeka kwe-SARS-COV-2, ngokusuka ekuvimbeleni kuya ekuvimbeleni, njengoba ukwanda okusheshayo okulindelekile kwenani lamacala kunganikeza abenzi bezinqumo nezibhedlela isikhathi esanele sokuqonda, ukwamukela nokulungisa izimpendulo zabo ngokufanele uma kungenziwanga ngaphambi kwesikhathi.
Ukuhlolwa okusheshayo kwengozi futhi kuchaza izinyathelo zezempilo zomphakathi zokunciphisa umthelela walolu bhubhane.
Kunesikhathi esifushane lapho amazwe enethuba lokulokhu ekhulisa imizamo yawo yokulawula ukuze kuncishiswe ukusakazeka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 futhi kuncishiswe ingcindezi ekunakekelweni kwezempilo.
Uma lokhu kungenzeki, kungenzeka ukuthi izinhlelo zokunakekelwa kwezempilo zamanye amazwe e-EU/EEA zizobhekana nokwanda kweziguli ezidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile ezinsukwini noma emasontweni azayo.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo i-Coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19), okubangelwa i-severe acute respiratory syndrome (SARS) coronavirus 2 (i-SARS-CoV-2), kuze kube manje sekubulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3,000 futhi kwaqubuka abangaphezu kuka-80,000 eChina nakwezinye izindawo emhlabeni, okuholele enhlekeleleni kubantu.
Njenge-virus yayo efanayo, i-SARS-CoV, eyabangela i-SARS kubantu abayizinkulungwane ngo-2003, i-SARS-CoV-2 nayo ingadluliselwa kumalulwane futhi ibangele izimpawu ezifanayo ngendlela efanayo.
Kodwa-ke, i-COVID-19 inobungozi obuphansi kanye nokufa kwe-SARS kodwa isakazeka kakhulu futhi ithinta abantu abadala kakhulu kunentsha futhi ithinta amadoda amaningi kunabesifazane.
Ngenxa yokwanda okusheshayo kwezincwadi eziphathelene nalesi sifo esivelayo, lesi sihloko sizama ukunikeza ukubuyekeza okufike ngesikhathi futhi okuphelele kwalolu daba lokucwaninga oluthuthuka ngokushesha.
Sizohlanganisa izinto eziyisisekelo mayelana ne-epidemiology, i-etiology, i-virology, ukuxilongwa, ukwelashwa, ukuvezwa kwesikhathi, kanye nokuvimbela lesi sifo.
Nakuba kunemibuzo eminingi esadinga izimpendulo, sinethemba lokuthi lokhu kubuyekezwa kuyasiza ekuqondeni nasekuqothulweni kwalesi sifo esisongelayo.
Umkhosi Wentwasahlobo wangoJanuwari 25, 2020 usuphenduke inkumbulo engavamile futhi engenakulibaleka kubo bonke abantu baseChina ababeshushiswa ukuba bahlale endlini kulo lonke leli holide futhi amasonto amaningi ngemuva kwalokho ngenxa yokuqubuka kwesifo esisha se-virus.
Leli gciwane lifana kakhulu ne-coronavirus (CoV) eyabangela ukuqubuka kwesifo esibi sokuphefumula (SARS) ngo-2003; ngakho-ke, i-World Health Organization (WHO) yabiza i-SARS-CoV-2 ngoFebhuwari 11, 2020, futhi isifo esihlobene naso sabizwa ngokuthi yi-Cov Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Lolu bhubhane lwaqala eWuhan, eChina, futhi lwasakazeka ngokushesha kulo lonke izwe nakweminye cishe engu-50 emhlabeni wonke.
Kusukela ngo-March 2, 2020, leli gciwane liye laholela emacaleni angaphezu kuka-80,000 aqinisekisiwe e-COVID-19, aneziguli ezingaphezu kuka-40,000 ezikhishwe futhi iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-3,000 ezifile.
I-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi i-COVID-19 i "yisitha somphakathi esingu-1" futhi inamandla kakhulu kunobuphekula.
Ngokwe-PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezinyanga ezimbili, sekushicilelwe amaphepha angaphezu kuka-200 ku-COVID-19 kuhlanganise ne-virology, i-epidemiology, i-etiology, ukuxilongwa, kanye nokwelashwa kusukela embikweni wokuqala ngoJanuwari 7, 2020 owawunqume ukulandelana kwegciwane elahlukaniswe ezigulini eziningi.
Lokhu kubuyekezwa kuzama ukufingqa inqubekela phambili yocwaningo emkhakheni omusha okhula ngokushesha.
Uma kungenzeka, sizozama ukuqhathanisa i-COVID-19 ne-SARS kanye nenye isifo esibangelwa i-Covid, i-Middle East respiratory syndrome (i-MERS, eyaqubuka ngo-2012).
Sizoxoxa nangalokho esikufundile kuze kube manje ngokuvimbela nokuphawula isifo kanye neminye imibuzo esaphakeme.
Ama-CoV ayebhekwa ngokwesiko njengamagciwane awona abulalayo kubantu, ikakhulukazi abangela cishe u-15% wokuthuthumela okuvamile 4.
Kodwa-ke, kuleli khulu leminyaka, sihlangane nama-CoVs abantu anesifo esibulalayo kakhulu kabili, okungukuthi, i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, okubangele ukuqubuka okokuqala eChina ngo-2003 naseSaudi Arabia ngo-2012, futhi ngokushesha kwasakazekela kwamanye amazwe amaningi anokuqubuka nokufa okubi.
Ngakho-ke, i-COVID-19 yamanje ingukuqubuka kwesithathu kwe-Covid emlandweni obhaliwe wabantu.
Njengoba kuboniswe kuFig. Fig.1,1, amaqoqo e-pneumonia anomsuka ongaziwa abikwa okokuqala e-Wuhan ngoDisemba 31, 2019 ku-National Health Commission yaseChina.
Ezinsukwini eziyisikhombisa kamuva ukulandelana kwe- CoV kwakhululwa.
NgoJanuwari 15, 2020 kwabikwa ukuthi umuntu wokuqala obulawe yi-Wuhan.
Phakathi naleso sikhathi, ubhubhane lwasakazekela ngokushesha emadolobheni, ezifundazweni nasemazweni angomakhelwane.
NgoJanuwari 20, kwabikwa ukuthi abantu abahlinzeka ngezempilo bathelelekile, okusikisela ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi abantu bangabhebhetheka.
NgoJanuwari 23, idolobha laseWuhan lavalwa futhi zonke izinto zokuhamba zomphakathi zamiswa.
NgoJanuwari 24 ucwaningo lokuqala lomtholampilo lwesifo lwabika ukuthi, ezigulini ezingu-41 ezinamacala aqinisekisiwe, abangu-21 kuphela abaxhumana ngqo nemakethe yaseWuhan yokudla kwasolwandle okwakubhekwa njengendawo yokuqala yokutheleleka okuvela kumthombo wesilwane ongaziwa.
Ngo-January 30, i-WHO yamemezela ukuthi lesi sifo siyisimo esiphuthumayo sezempilo somhlaba wonke.
