Umkhuhlane uvame ukuba uphawu oluyinhloko nolokuqala lwe-COVID-19, olungahambisana nokungabi nazimpawu noma ezinye izimpawu ezifana nokukhwehlela okomile, ukuphefumula kanzima, ubuhlungu bemisipha, isiyezi, ikhanda, umphimbo obuhlungu, i-rhinorrhea, ubuhlungu besifuba, isifo sohudo, isicanucanu, nokuhlanza.
Ezinye iziguli zabhekana ne-dyspnea kanye/ noma ne-hypoxemia isonto elilodwa ngemva kokuqala kwesifo.
Ezimweni ezinzima, iziguli zasheshe zathuthuka zaba i- acute respiratory syndrome, septic shock, metabolic acidosis, kanye ne- coagulopathy.
Iziguli ezinomkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula nomkhuhlane osheshayo, ngisho noma zingenakho ukungajwayelekile kokuthwebula amaphaphu, kufanele zihlolwe igciwane ukuze zitholakale ngokushesha.
Ucwaningo olwenziwe ngasekupheleni kukaDisemba 2019 lwabonisa ukuthi amaphesenti ezimpawu ayeyi-98% yomkhuhlane, 76% yesikhwehlela esomile, 55% ye-dyspnea, kanye ne-3% yesifo sohudo; 8% weziguli zidinga ukwesekwa kokuphefumula.
Imiphumela efanayo yabikwa ezifundweni ezimbili zakamuva ezihlanganisa umndeni kanye neqembu elibangelwa ukudluliselwa komdlavuza kumuntu ongenazo izimpawu.
Ngokuqhathaniswa, ucwaningo olwenziwa ngo-2012 lwabonisa ukuthi iziguli ezine-MERS-CoV nazo zazinomkhuhlane (i-98%), ukukhwehlela okomile (i-47%), kanye ne-dyspnea (i-55%) njengezimpawu zazo eziyinhloko.
Kodwa-ke, u-80% wabo wayedinga ukwesekwa ngumoya, okuyi-MERS ebulala kakhulu kune-COVID-19.
