La ma-cytokine enza amangqamuzana omzimba avule inqwaba yama-radical free (amagciwane) okuyiwona abangela i-ARDS kanye nokuhluleka kwezitho eziningi.
Ukucindezela amasosha omzimba kubalulekile ekwelapheni iziphepho ze-cytokine, ikakhulukazi ezigulini ezinzima.
Ama-corticosteroid kanye ne-tocilizumab, i-anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody, kuye kwasetshenziswa ekwelapheni isivunguvungu se-cytokine.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha ezicindezela amasosha omzimba ezibhekene ne-cytokine storm zihlanganisa ukuguqulwa kwempendulo yomzimba eqondiswe ngamangqamuzana e-T; ukuvimba kwe-IFN-γ, IL-1, ne-TNF; ukuvimbela i-JAK; i-blinatumomab; ukucindezela ukuhanjiswa kwesiginali ye-cytokine 4; kanye nama-HDAC inhibitor.
Ama-steroid, njengama-immunosuppressant, asetshenziswa kakhulu ekwelapheni i-SARS ukuze kuncishiswe ukuqina komonakalo wokuvuvukala.
Kodwa-ke, ama-steroid ngemithamo ephezulu awazange abe nomthelela omuhle ekulimaleni kwamaphaphu okunzima ezigulini ezine-SARS ne-COVID-19.
Kunalokho, zingabangela imiphumela emibi, ikakhulukazi i-osteonecrosis ye-avascular, ezithinta kakhulu isimo.
Noma kunjalo, kunconywe ukuba kusetshenziswe ngokuqapha iziguli ze-COVID-19 ezigula kakhulu, ngemithamo emincane kuya emincane.
Ngesikhathi sokubhala le ncwadi, akukho ukwelashwa okuphumelelayo kwegciwane okuqinisekisiwe.
Kodwa-ke, ukwelashwa nge-remdesivir, i-nucleotide analogue, kwatholakala ukuthi kuyasebenza kumuntu waseMelika onesifo i-COVID-19.
I-Remdesivir iwumuthi omusha olwa namagciwane owasungulwa iGilead ekuqaleni ukuze kwelashwe izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane e-Ebola ne-Marlburg.
Kamuva, i-remdesivir yabonisa nokuthi kungenzeka ivimbe amanye amagciwane e-RNA ane-stranded eyodwa kuhlanganise namagciwane e-MERS ne-SARS.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, iGilead inikeze iChina le nhlanganisela ukuze yenze izivivinyo ezimbili kubantu abangenwe yi-SARS-CoV-2, futhi imiphumela ilindelwe kakhulu.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i- baricitinb, i- interferon-α, i- lopinavir/ ritonavir, ne- ribavirin kuye kwasikiselwa njengokwelashwa okungenzeka kweziguli ezinezimpawu zokuphefumula ezibucayi.
Ukuhlanza, isicanucanu, ukuhlanza, ukulimala kwesibindi, nezinye izimpawu ezingathandeki zingavela ngemva kokwelashwa okuhlangene ne-lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Ukuhlangana kwalezi zindlela zokwelapha nezinye izidakamizwa ezisetshenziswa ezigulini kufanele kuhlolwe ngokucophelela.
I-Plasma evela ezigulini eziphulukisiwe kanye nokukhiqizwa kwama-antibody
Ukuqoqwa kwegazi leziguli ezingasenaso isifo esithathelwanayo ukuze kwelashwe ezinye iziguli ezinesifo esifanayo noma ukuze kuvikelwe abantu abaphilile ekubambeni lesi sifo sekunesikhathi eside kwenzeka.
Ngempela, iziguli eziye zaluleka ngokuvamile zinamazinga aphakeme kakhulu emagciwane alwa namagciwane egazini lazo.
Ama-antibody yi-immunoglobulin (Ig) ekhiqizwa ama-B lymphocyte ukuze alwe namagciwane nezinye izinto ezingaziwa futhi ayazi ukuthi kunama-molecule akhethekile kula magciwane futhi ayawabulala ngokuqondile.
Ngokusekelwe kulokhu, i-plasma yathathwa egazini leqembu leziguli ezalulama ku-COVID-19 futhi yafakelwa ezigulini eziyi-10 ezazigula kakhulu.
Izimpawu zabo zabuna zingakapheli amahora angu-24, zihambisana nokunciphisa ukuvuvukala kanye nomthwalo wegciwane kanye nokuthuthuka kokugcwala komoya-mpilo egazini.
Nokho, ukuhlola nokucacisa kuyadingeka ukuze kwenziwe isiphakamiso sokuthi le ndlela ingasetshenziswa ngezinga elikhulu ngaphambi kokuba kusungulwe izindlela zokwelapha eziqondile.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ngenxa yemiphumela yokwelapha, ezinye zezinto ezingalungile ezihambisana ne-plasma kufanele zicatshangelwe ngokucophelela.
Isibonelo, ama-antibodies angavuselela kakhulu ukuphendula kwamasosha omzimba futhi abangele i-cytokine release syndrome, okungaba ubuthi obungaba yingozi empilweni.
Ukugxila kwama-antibody egazini ngokuvamile kuphansi, futhi kudingeka i-plasma eningi ekwelapheni iziguli ezigula kakhulu.
Kunzima ukuthuthukisa nokukhiqiza amasosha omzimba athile ngokushesha ngokwanele ukuze kulwe nobhadane lomhlaba wonke.
Ngakho-ke, kubaluleke kakhulu futhi kuyasebenza ukuhlukanisa amaseli e-B ezigulini eziphulukisiwe bese kutholakala amakhodi e-genetic afaka ama-antibodies asebenzayo noma ukuhlolwa kwama-antibodies asebenzayo amelana namaprotheni abalulekile egciwane.
Ngale ndlela, singakwazi ukukhulisa ukukhiqizwa kwama-antibody.
I-TCM isetshenziselwe ukwelapha izifo ezihlukahlukene eChina izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Nokho, imiphumela yayo incike kakhulu ekuhlanganisweni kwezingxenye eziningi emthonjeni ohlukahluka kuye ngokuxilongwa kwesifo okusekelwe emibonweni ye-TCM.
Iningi lezakhi ezisebenzayo lisaziwa noma alicaci ngoba kunzima ukuzikhipha nokuziqinisekisa noma ukuhlanganisa kwazo okuhle kakhulu.
Okwamanje, ngenxa yokuntuleka kokwelashwa okuphumelelayo nokuqondile kwe-COVID-19, i-TCM isibe enye yezindlela zokwelapha eziyinhloko ezigulini ezinezimpawu ezincane kuya kweziphakathi noma kulabo abasinde ezigabeni ezibucayi.
Isibonelo, amakhuphula eShu Feng Jie Du kanye nama Lian Hua Qing Wen atholakala ukuthi asebenza ngempumelelo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Izinga eliphakeme kakhulu lokulashwa kweziguli ze-COVID-19 labhekwa ezifundazweni eziningana eChina ezazisebenzisa i-TCM ezigulini zazo ezingu-87%, kufaka phakathi iGansu (63.7%), iNingxia (50%), neHunan (50%), kanti isifundazwe saseHubei, esasisebenzisa i-TCM ezigulini ze-COVID-19 ezingaba ngu-30% kuphela, sasinenani eliphansi kakhulu lokulashwa (13%).
Nokho, lokhu kuqhathanisa okunzima kakhulu njengoba kunezinye izici eziningi eziyimbangela, njengenombolo nobunzima beziguli, okufanele zifakwe ekuhloleni.
Ngo-February 18, 2020, uBoli Zhang kanye nozakwabo bashicilela ucwaningo lokuqhathanisa ukwelashwa kwe-western medicine (WM) kuphela nokwelashwa okuhlanganisiwe kwe-WM ne-TCM.
Bathola ukuthi izikhathi ezidingekayo ukuze kuvuselelwe izinga lokushisa komzimba, ukunyamalala kwezimpawu, nokufakwa esibhedlela kwakunciphe kakhulu eqenjini le- WM+TCM kunakuleli le- WM kuphela.
Okuhlaba umxhwele kakhulu, izinga lokwehla kwezimpawu (kusuka kokulula kuya kokunzima) laliphansi kakhulu eqenjini le-WM + TCM kunelali-WM kuphela (7.4% uma kuqhathaniswa no-46.2%) futhi izinga lokufa laliphansi eqenjini le-WM + TCM kunelali-WM kuphela (8.8% uma kuqhathaniswa no-39%).
Noma kunjalo, kusadingeka ukuba kwenziwe izivivinyo ezilawulwa kangcono ngezinga elikhulu nangamasevisi amaningi ukuze kutholakale ukuthi i-TCM isebenza kahle futhi iphephile yini.
Kungaba okuthakazelisayo futhi ukuchaza indlela izenzo ezisebenza ngayo nokucacisa izingxenye eziphumelelayo zokwelashwa kwe-TCM noma ukuhlanganiswa kwazo uma kungenzeka.
Iziguli ezisolwayo noma eziqinisekisiwe ukuthi zine-COVID-19 ngokuvamile zesaba kakhulu lesi sifo esithathelwanayo esibulalayo, futhi abantu abavalelwe bodwa nabo bazizwa benesithukuthezi, benesizungu futhi bethukuthele.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izimpawu zokutheleleka ezifana nomkhuhlane, i-hypoxia, nokukhwehlela kanye nemiphumela emibi yokwelashwa njengokungalali okubangelwa ama-corticosteroid kungaholela ekukhathazekeni nasekuhluphekeni kwengqondo.
Esigabeni sokuqala sokuqubuka kwe-SARS, kwabhekwa izinkinga eziningi zengqondo ezihlanganisa ukucindezeleka okungapheli, ukukhathazeka, ukuhlaselwa wukuphazamiseka, ukuphazamiseka kwengqondo, izimpawu zokuphazamiseka kwengqondo, ukuhlanya, ngisho nokuzibulala.
Ukufuna ukuhlangana nabantu nokuvalela abantu bodwa, njengengxenye yezindlela zokuphepha zomphakathi zokubhekana nokuqubuka kwe-COVID-19, kungenza abantu babe novalo futhi bazizwe benecala ngemiphumela yokutheleleka, ukuvalelwa bodwa, kanye nokucwaswa emindenini yabo nakubangane.
Ngakho, ukunakekelwa kwempilo yengqondo kufanele kunikezwe iziguli ze-COVID-19, abantu abasolwayo, nabantu abaxhumana nabo kanye nomphakathi jikelele oswele.
Ukwesekwa ngokwengqondo kufanele kufake ukusungulwa kwamaqembu ezempilo yengqondo ahlukahlukene, ukuxhumana okucacile okunezibuyekezo ezijwayelekile nezinembile mayelana nokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nezinhlelo zokwelashwa kanye nokusetshenziswa kwamadivayisi nezinhlelo zokusebenza zobuchwepheshe ukuze kugwenywe ukuthintana eduze komunye nomunye.
Imigomo yokugoma esebenzayo ibalulekile ekuphazamiseni uchungechunge lokudluliselwa kusuka ezinqolobaneni zezilwane nakubantu abangenwe yizifo kuya ezindlini eziyingozi futhi imvamisa ihlanganisa ukwelashwa okulwa namagciwane ekulawuleni ubhubhane olubangelwa amagciwane amasha.
Kwenziwe imizamo yokwakha imithi yokugoma esekelwe ku-S protein ukuze kukhiqizwe amasosha omzimba anqanda ukugula futhi/noma avikelayo ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV.
Imithi yokugoma e-live-attenuated iye yahlolwa ezimweni zezilwane ze-SARS.
Nokho, ukusebenza kwe- in vivo kwalezi zibhamu ezinconywayo kubantu asebekhulile kanye nemodeli yokubulala kanye nokuvikelwa kwazo ngokumelene nokutheleleka ngegciwane le- zoonotic kusazoqalwa ngaphambi kokuba kuqale ucwaningo lomtholampilo.
Lokhu kungenzeka kungenxa yokuthi i-SARS yaphela eminyakeni engu-17 edlule futhi akukho macala amasha abikiwe kusukela ngaleso sikhathi.
