Amasu okugoma asethuthukisiwe nge-MERS ngokusebenzisa igciwane elingasebenzi, i-DNA plasmids, ama-virus vectors, ama-nanoparticles, izinhlayiya ezifana negciwane kanye nama-protein subunits futhi amanye ahlolwe kumamodeli ezilwane.
Ukuthuthukiswa komuthi wokugoma ophephile futhi osebenzayo ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu abangenaso isifo somzimba kungumsebenzi ophuthumayo futhi obalulekile wokulawula ubhubhane oluqhubekayo.
Kodwa-ke, kuyinselele ukunqoba le nkinga ngenxa yesikhathi eside (esilinganiselwa ezinyangeni ezingu-18) esidingekayo ekuthuthukiseni umuthi wokugoma kanye nokwehlukahluka kwama-Cov.
