Ngakho-ke, abahlinzeka ngezempilo kufanele bagqoke izivikelo zobuso ezibonakalayo noma izibuko lapho besebenza neziguli.
Kumphakathi jikelele ezindaweni ezithintekile noma ezingathinteka, kunconywa kakhulu ukuthi wonke umuntu ageze izandla zakhe ngensipho yokubulala amagciwane kaningi kunokujwayelekile, azame ukuhlala endlini ukuze azihlukanise futhi anciphise ukuxhumana nabantu abangase batheleleke.
Ukude ngamamitha amathathu kubhekwa njengendawo efanelekile yokuba abantu bahlale kude nesiguli.
Lezi zinyathelo ziyizindlela eziphumelelayo zokunciphisa ingozi yokutheleleka kanye nokuvimbela ukusabalala kwegciwane.
Nakuba i-SARS-CoV-2 yafika njengegciwane elisha emhlabeni wabantu, ukufana kwayo okuphezulu ne-SARS-CoV njengoba kwabikwa ngo-7 kuJanuwari 2020 bekufanele kubangele ukuqapha okuphezulu eChina ngokususelwa enkumbulweni yayo ejulile yokuqubuka kwe-SARS ngo-2003.
Kodwa-ke, kwaze kwaba ngo-19 Januwari 2020 lapho umqondisi weCenter of Disease Control of Wuhan aduduza izakhamuzi ngokuthi leligciwane elisha linokutheleleka okuncane kanye nokwanda okulinganiselwe kusuka kumuntu kuye komunye nokuthi akuyona inkinga ukuvimbela nokulawula lesi sifo.
Lo myalezo wakhulula kakhulu abantu, ikakhulukazi ngesikhathi izwe lonke lilungiselela uMkhosi Wentwasahlobo, futhi isikhathi esibucayi sasidlulile ukuvimba lesi sifo esincane kakhulu eWuhan.
Ama-ejensi okulawula izifo eChina angase athathe lesi sifundo esinzima futhi enze intuthuko ebalulekile esikhathini esizayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, lezi zinhlaka kufanele (1) ziqaphe kakhulu lapho zenza izimemezelo zomphakathi njengoba wonke amazwi ebalulekile ezakhamuzini futhi engashintsha isimo sazo sengqondo nezinqumo; (2) zibe nengqondo futhi zisabele ngokushesha emibikweni engajwayelekile evela emtholampilo kunokulinda imibiko esemthethweni evela kodokotela noma izikhulu; (3) ziqine kakhulu ekuvimbeleni ubhubhane olungaba khona lapho lusesigabeni salo sokuqala kunokuba zizame ukududuza umphakathi; futhi (4) zivame ukukhipha izivivinyo ezihloselwe futhi eziphumelelayo zokukhulisa ukuqwashisa komphakathi ngezifo eziwumshayabhuqe nokuhlola nokuthuthukisa uhlelo lokuphendula lomphakathi ngezikhathi ezithile.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 okubangelwa yigciwane elisha i-SARS-CoV-2 kwaqala ekupheleni kukaDisemba 2019.
Ezinyangeni ezingaphansi kwezintathu, isisakazeke kulo lonke elaseChina nakwamanye amazwe acishe abe ngu-50 emhlabeni wonke ngesikhathi sokubhalwa kwalokhu.
Njengoba igciwane lifana kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV futhi nezimpawu zifana phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kudale umuzwa wokuthi i-SARS iyaphinda.
Nokho, kunomehluko ophawulekayo phakathi kwe-COVID-19 ne-SARS, obalulekile ekuvimbeleni ubhubhane nasekwelapheni iziguli.
I-COVID-19 ithinta abantu abadala kakhulu kunentsha futhi ithinta amadoda kakhulu kunabesifazane, kanti izinga lobungozi nokufa kwabantu asebekhulile nalo liphakeme kunentsha.
I-SARS inezinga lokufa eliphakeme kune-COVID-19 (10.91% uma kuqhathaniswa ne-1.44%).
Iziguli ze-COVID-19 zidlulisela igciwane ngisho noma zingenayo imikhondo, kanti iziguli ze-SARS zivame ukwenza lokhu uma zigula kakhulu, okubangela ubunzima obukhulu kakhulu bokunqanda ukusabalala kwe-COVID-19 kune-SARS.
Lokhu kuchaza ngokwengxenye ukuthi kungani i-SARS-CoV-2 isakazeka ngokushesha futhi kabanzi kune-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlolwa okuvamile kwe-RNA kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungaba okungekho kwabathile abane-COVID-19.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, iziguli eziphulukisiwe zingabuye zibe ne-virus.
Lokhu okutholakele kwandisa kakhulu ingozi yokusakazeka kwegciwane.
Ngenxa yenqubekela phambili esheshayo yocwaningo lwe-COVID-19, kusasele izinkinga ezimbalwa ezibalulekile okufanele zixazululwe, njengokulandelayo:
I-SARS-CoV-2 yavela kuphi?
Yize kutholakale i-96% ye-genetic homologue phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 nama-CoV amabili afana ne-bat SARS, namanje asikwazi ukuphetha ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela kumalulwane.
Yisiphi isilwane esasingumuntu wasendulo esasidlulisela abantu igciwane lisuka kumuntu wokuqala, njengamalulwane?
Ngaphandle kokwazi izimpendulo eziya ku- #1 no- 2, asikwazi ukuvimba ukudluliswa, futhi ukuqubuka kungabuye kwenzeke noma nini.
Nakuba ukulinganisa kwamagciwane kanye nokuhlolwa kwe-biochemical kuye kwabonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ibopha i-ACE2, igciwane lingena kanjani ngqo kumaseli omgudu womoya futhi libangele izinguquko ezilandelayo ze-pathological?
Ingabe leli gciwane liyabopha futhi amangqamuzana akhipha i-ACE2 kwezinye izitho?
Ngaphandle kwezimpendulo ezicacile zale mibuzo, ngeke sikwazi ukuthola ngokushesha isifo ngokunembile futhi sithole nokwelashwa okuphumelelayo.
Lesi sifo sizoba khona isikhathi eside kangakanani?
Igciwane liguquka kanjani ngokwemvelo ngesikhathi lisakazeka kubantu?
Ingabe iyoba umqedazwe emhlabeni wonke, ingabe iyophela njenge-SARS noma ingabe iyobuyela emuva ngezikhathi ezithile njengegciwane lomkhuhlane?
Kubalulekile kodwa kungathatha isikhathi ukufuna izimpendulo zale mibuzo engenhla neminye eminingi.
Nokho, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi kudingani, akukho okunye esingakwenza ngaphandle kokumisa ubhubhane ngokushesha ngangokunokwenzeka futhi sibuyisele ukuphila kwethu kokujwayelekile.
Imvelaphi ye-zoonoses yamakhorona-virus abantu
Ukuguquka kwesimo nokuguquguquka kwezinto kuye kwaholela ekuguqukeni kwe-coronaviruses (CoVs) kanye nezibambiso zazo, kuhlanganise nabantu, izinkulungwane zeminyaka.
Ngaphambi kuka-2003, ama-CoV amabili esintu (ama-HCoV) ayaziwa ukuthi abangela izifo ezingatheni, njengokubanda okuvamile.
Ukuqubuka kwesifo sokuphefumula esibi kakhulu (i-SARS) kanye nesifo sokuphefumula esibi kakhulu (i-MERS) eMiddle East sekuphenduke umthelela wokudalula ukuthi ukutheleleka nge-HCoV kungaba yingozi kangakanani futhi kusongele ukuphila.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 enkabeni yeChina ekupheleni kuka-2019 kuye kwaphinde kwafaka ama-CoV endaweni evelele futhi kwasimangaza ngokudluliselwa kwayo okuphezulu kodwa nokunciphisa amandla okubangela izifo uma kuqhathaniswa no-SARS-CoV udadewabo.
Ukutheleleka nge-HCoV kuyisifo esivela ezilwaneni futhi ukuqonda imvelaphi ye-HCoVs evela ezilwaneni kungasisiza kakhulu.
Iningi lama-CoV livela kumalulwane lapho engalethi khona izifo.
Ama-reservoir host aphakathi kwamanye ama-HCoV nawo ayaziwa.
Ukuhlonza izilwane ezifuywayo kunemiphumela eqondile ekuvimbeleni izifo zabantu.
Ukuhlola ukusebenzelana kwe-Cov-host ezilwaneni kungathola nokuqonda okubalulekile nge-Cov pathogenesis kubantu.
Kulokhu kubuyekezwa, siveza ukubuka konke kolwazi olukhona mayelana nama-HCV ayisikhombisa, ngokugxila emlandweni wokutholakala kwawo kanye nemvelaphi yawo ye-zoonotic nokudluliselwa phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Okubaluleke kakhulu, siqhathanisa futhi siqhathanisa ama-HCoV ahlukene ngokombono wokuziphendukela kwegciwane nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-genome.
Lesi sifo se-COV 2019 (i-COVID-19) sikhulunywa ngaso kulesi sihloko.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, kugqanyiswa nezimfuneko zokushintsha ngempumelelo isilwane esinomdlavuza kanye nemiphumela yokuziphendukela kwegciwane ebucayi besifo.
Ama-Coronaviruses (ama-CoV) angawomndeni we-Coronaviridae, ohlanganisa iqembu lamagciwane e-RNA ahlanganiswe, anokuzwela okuhle, anentambo eyodwa.
Lawa magciwane ane-genome enkulu kunazo zonke yama-kilobase angu-26 kuya kwangu-32 phakathi kwamagciwane e-RNA abizwa ngokuthi CoVs ngenxa ye-morphology yawo efana nomqhele ngaphansi kwe-electron microscope.
Ngokwesakhiwo, ama-CoV anezinhlayiya zofuzo ezingehlukanisiwe ezihlanganyela inhlangano efanayo.
Cishe izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu ze-genome ziqukethe amafreyimu amabili amakhulu avulekile okufunda (i-ORF1a ne-ORF1b), ahunyushelwa kuma-ppp1a nama-ppp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Ama-polyproteins ayaqhubeka nokulungiswa ukuze akhiqize amaprotheni angu-16 angenawo ukwakheka, abizwa ngokuthi nsp1~16.
Ingxenye esele ye-genome iqukethe ama-ORF amaprotheni ahlobene nesakhiwo, kuhlanganise ne-spike (S), i-envelope (E), ulwelwesi (M) ne-nucleoprotein (N).
Inani lamaprotheni angawokuzalwa ahlukile nawo afakwa kumakhodi ngemikhiqizo ehlukene yama-CoV.
Ngokuya ngomehluko wokulandelana kwamaprotheni, ama-Cov ahlukaniswa abe yizigaba ezine (i-alpha-CoV, i-beta-CoV, i-gamma-CoV ne-delta-CoV), phakathi kwazo izigaba ze-beta-CoV ziqukethe ama-HCoV amaningi futhi zihlukaniswe zibe yizigaba ezine (i-A, B, C ne-D).
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bukhombisile ukuthi amalulwane nezilwane ezincelisayo ziwumthombo wamagciwane we-alpha-CoVs kanye ne-beta-CoVs, kanti izinyoni ziwumthombo oyinhloko wama-gamma-CoVs kanye nama-delta-CoVs.
Izinkulungwane zeminyaka, ama-CoV aye ewela njalo imigoqo yezinhlobo futhi amanye aye avele njengamagciwane abalulekile okubulala izifo kubantu.
Kuze kube manje, ama-CoV ayisikhombisa abantu (ama-HCoV) ayaziwa.
Phakathi kwazo i-alpha-CoVs yi-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-NL63.
Amanye ama-beta-CoV amahlanu ahlanganisa i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1, i-coronavirus ye-acute respiratory syndrome (SARS-CoV), i-coronavirus ye-Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS-CoV) kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2.
I-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 ne-HCoV-NL63 ngokuvamile zibangela izimpawu ezincane, njengokuthuthumela komkhuhlane noma isifo sohudo.
Ngokuphambene, i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 esanda kutholakala inesifo esibulalayo kakhulu, okubangela ukutheleleka okunzima kwezindlela zokuphefumula ezingezansi ezigulini eziningi kakhulu ezinethuba eliphakeme lokuthola i-acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS) kanye nokuvela kwemiphumela engaphandle kwamaphaphu.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E, i-B814, lwahlukaniswa nokukhishwa komphimbo ezigulini ezibandayo maphakathi nawo-1960.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, ulwazi olwengeziwe lwaqoqwa ngokucwaninga kabanzi nge-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, zombili ezibangela izimpawu ezizimele.
Ngempela, umqondo wawamukelwa kabanzi wokuthi ukutheleleka ngama-CoV ngokuvamile akunangozi kuze kube ukuqubuka kwe-SARS.
Ukuqubuka kwe-SARS okwenzeka ngo-2003 kungenye yezinhlekelele ezedlule emlandweni, kwabulala abantu abangaphezu kuka-8 000 kanti inani elibulalayo lacishe lafinyelela ku-10%.
Eminyakeni eyishumi kamuva, ukuqubuka kwe-Middle East respiratory syndrome (MERS) kwaphumela ekubeni kube nomqedazwe ohlala njalo eNhlonhlweni yase-Arabia nokusabalala okwenzeka ngezikhathi ezithile ezweni lonke.
I-novel HCoV 2019 (2019-nCoV), eyashintshwa kamuva igama yaba yi-SARS-CoV-2, iyona ebangela ubhubhane lwesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) esiqhubekayo, esibulale abantu abangaphezu kuka-3,120 futhi sathelela abantu abangaphezu kuka-91 000 kusukela ngo-March 3, 2020.
Sekulokhu kuzwakala i-alamu futhi umhlaba kumele ulungiselele ubhubhane oluzayo lwe-SARS-CoV-2.
Zonke lezi-HCoV eziyisikhombisa zivela emagundane, amagundane noma ezilwaneni zasekhaya.
Imigqa eminingi yobufakazi isekela imvelaphi yokuziphendukela kwemvelo yawo wonke ama-HCVs avela kumalulwane, lapho amagciwane evumelana kahle futhi engenazifo kodwa abonisa ukwehluka okukhulu kofuzo.
Ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 luye lwaletha izinselele ezinkulu kwezokwelapha, kwezesayensi, kwezenhlalo nezokuziphatha eChina nasemhlabeni wonke.
Ukuhlola imvelaphi ye-zoonotic yama-HCoV kunikeza uhlaka lokuqonda umlando wemvelo, amandla okuqhuba kanye nezici ezivimbela ukuqhuma kwezinhlobo.
Lokhu kungase kuqondise noma kusize ekufuneni indawo yokugcina, isilwane esiphakathi nesiphakamisayo (s) se-SARS-CoV-2, okuzoba nemithelela ebalulekile ekuvimbeleni ukuqubuka esikhathini esizayo.
Kulesi sibuyekezo siveza ukubuka konke kwemvelaphi ye-zoonotic, ukudluliswa kwe-interspecies kanye ne-pathogenesis yama-HCV.
Ikakhulu, sigcizelela futhi sixoxe ngendaba evamile yokuthi amagciwane omzali we-HCoVs ngokuvamile awawona amagciwane emizini yawo yemvelo kodwa aba amagciwane ngemva kokudluliselwa komunye umhlobo kumuntu omusha.
Siphinde sibuyise ukuthambekela kokuziphendukela kwemvelo kwe-HCoV lapho ukwanda kokudluliseka kuvame ukuza nokwehla kokubangela izifo.
Umphumela wokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 okuqhubekayo nawo kuxoxwa ngawo kulokhu.
Ama-Animal CoVs ayaziwa kusukela ngasekupheleni kwawo-1930.
Ngaphambi kokuhlukaniswa kokuqala kwe-HCoV-229E uhlobo B814 kusuka ekukhuphuleni kwamakhala eziguli ezazinokuthuthwa umkhuhlane, ama-CoV ahlukile ayekade ehlukanisiwe ezilwaneni ezahlukahlukene ezithelelekile, kufaka phakathi i-turkey, igundane, inkomo, ingulube, ikati nenja.
Emashumini eminyaka adlule, sekutholakale ama-HCV angu-7.
Ukufingqa kafushane umlando wokutholwa kwe-HCoV ngokulandelana kwesikhathi (Ithebula 1) kungaba ngolwazi futhi kube nemfundo.
Uhlobo lokuqala lwe-HCoV-229E lwahlukaniswa emgqeni wokuphefumula weziguli ezinegciwane lemigqa ephezulu yokuphefumula ngonyaka ka-1966, futhi kamuva lwasetshenziselwa ukukhula emigqeni yamangqamuzana amaphunga e-WI-38.
Iziguli ezitheleleke nge-HCoV-229E zaveza izimpawu ezijwayelekile zokubanda, ezihlanganisa ikhanda, ukucasuka, ukungaphatheki kahle kanye nomphimbo obuhlungu, nomkhuhlane nokukhwehlela okubonwe ezimweni eziyi-10~20%.
Kamuva ngo-1967, i-HCoV-OC43 yahlukaniswa kusuka kumasiko ezithelo nokudlula okulandelanayo ebuchosheni bamagundane ancelayo.
Izici zomtholampilo zokutheleleka kwe-HCoV-OC43 zibonakala zifana nalezo ezibangelwa yi-HCoV-229E, okungakwazi ukuhlukaniswa ngokwezibonakaliso nokutheleleka nezinye izifo zokuphefumula ezifana namagciwane omkhuhlane A nama-rhinovirus.
Kokubili i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43 zisatshalaliswa emhlabeni wonke, futhi zivame ukudluliselwa ikakhulukazi ngesikhathi sasebusika esimweni sezulu esipholile.
Ngokuvamile, isikhathi sokufukamela la magciwane amabili singaphansi kwesonto elilodwa, bese kulandela ukugula okungamasonto amabili.
Ngokwesifundo esiphathelene nabantu abavolontiya, abantu abaphilile abanegciwane le-HCoV-229E baqala ukuba nomkhuhlane omncane.
Iziguli ezimbalwa kuphela ezinamasosha omzimba abuthakathaka zabonisa ukutheleleka okunzima emigwaqweni yokuphefumula engezansi.
I-SARS, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-pneumonia engajwayelekile, yaba ubhubhane lokuqala olwabikwa kahle olwalubangelwa yi-HCoV emlandweni wesintu kanti i-ejensi ye-etiological yi-SARS-CoV, i-HCoV yesithathu etholakele.
Icala lokuqala le-SARS lingalandelwa emuva ekupheleni kuka-2002 esifundazweni saseGuangdong eChina.
Umqedazwe we-SARS wabangela ukuba kubikwe amacala angu-8 096 kanye nokufa kwabantu abangu-774, okwasakazeka emazweni amaningi nasemazwekazini.
Ngaphandle kwalezi zigciwane ezisakaza kakhulu, kwacatshangwa ukuthi icala ngalinye lingaholela ezimweni ezimbili eziphindwe kabili, nesikhathi sokufukamela esiyizinsuku ezi-4 kuya kwezi-7 kanye nenani eliphakeme le-virus load elivela ngosuku lwe-10 lokugula.
Iziguli ezitheleleke nge-SARS-CoV ekuqaleni zine-myalgia, ikhanda, imfiva, ukungaphatheki kahle kanye nokuthuthumela, kulandelwa ukuphefumula kabi, ukukhwehlela kanye nokuphefumula kanzima njengezimpawu zakamuva.
I-Lymphopenia, ukuphazamiseka kokuhlolwa kokusebenza kwesibindi, kanye nokwenyuka kwe-creatine kinase kuyizimpawu ezivamile eziphambene nomthetho ezibonwa e-SARS.
Ukulimala kwe- alveolar okukhishwe, ukwanda kwamaseli e- epithelial kanye nokwanda kwama- macrophages nakho kuyabonwa ezigulini ze- SARS.
Cishe i-20% kuya ku-30% yeziguli kamuva zidinga ukunakekelwa okujulile nokuhlinzwa ngemishini.
Ngaphezu kwendlela yokuphefumula engezansi, izitho eziningi ezihlanganisa indlela yokugaya ukudla, isibindi nezinso nazo zingase zithinteke kulezi zimo ezinzima, ngokuvamile zihambisana nesiphepho se-cytokine, esingaba esibulalayo ikakhulukazi ezigulini ezinomzimba ongasebenzi kahle.
Igciwane laqala ukuhlukaniswa kusuka ekuhlolweni kwamaphaphu okuvulekile kwesihlobo sesiguli esiyisihluthulelo esahamba saya eHong Kong sisuka eGuangzhou.
Kusukela ngaleso sikhathi, imizamo emikhulu iye yazinikezelwa ekucwaningeni i-HCoV.
I-HCoV-NL63 yahlukaniswa nengane enezinyanga ezingu-7 yaseNetherlands ngasekupheleni kuka-2004.
Ekuqaleni kwatholakala ukuthi yayandile ezinganeni ezincane, asebekhulile nasezigulini ezinokulimala kwamasosha omzimba eziphethwe izifo zokuphefumula.
Ukuvela kwe-coryza, i-conjunctivitis, umkhuhlane, kanye ne-bronchiolitis kuvamile esifweni esibangelwa i-HCoV-NL63.
Olunye ucwaningo oluzimele lwachaza ukuhlukaniswa kwegciwane elifanayo kusuka esibonelweni somphunga esivela kumfanyana onezinyanga eziyi-8 onesifo samaphaphu eNetherlands.
Nakuba yabonwa eNetherlands, empeleni isakazeka emhlabeni wonke.
Kulinganiselwa ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 idala cishe u-4.7% wezifo ezivamile zokuphefumula, futhi ukuqubuka kwayo okuphezulu kwenzeka ekuqaleni kwehlobo, entwasahlobo nasebusika.
I-HCoV-NL63 ihlotshaniswa ne-obstructive laryngitis, eyaziwa nangokuthi i-croup.
Ngalowo nyaka, i-HCoV-HKU1 yahlukaniswa nendoda eneminyaka engu-71 ubudala eyayigcinwe esibhedlela ngenxa ye-pneumonia ne-bronchiolitis eHong Kong.
Ngaphandle kwe-pneumonia kanye ne-bronchiolitis etholakala emphakathini, i-HCoV-HKU1 yabikwa ukuthi ihlobene nokuqubuka kwesifuba somoya.
Ngokufanayo ne-HCoV-NL63, i-HCoV-229E ne-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-HKU1 yatholakala emhlabeni wonke, yabangela izifo zokuphefumula ezincane.
Wonke la ma-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini azivumelanise kahle nabantu futhi ngokuvamile mancane amathuba okuba aguquke abe izifo ezibulalayo kakhulu, yize izingozi zenzeka ngezizathu ezingaziwa njengasesimweni esingajwayelekile sohlobo oluncane lwe-HCoV-NL63, okusanda kubikwa ukuthi lubangela ukutheleleka okunzima komgudu wokuphefumula ophansi eChina.
Ngokuvamile, uma la ma-HCoVs ethola ikhono lokudlulisela ngokuphumelelayo futhi azigcine ngokuqhubekayo kubantu, nawo aba mancane kakhulu noma awabi namagciwane.
I-MERS-CoV yaqala ukuhlukaniswa ngo-2012 kumaphaphu wesiguli esineminyaka engu-60 ubudala esathuthuka i-pneumonia eyingozi kanye nokuhluleka kwezinso eSaudi Arabia.
Nakuba iningi lamacala aqinisekiswe elebhu evela eMpumalanga Ephakathi, amacala angenisiwe anezifo ezisakazeka ngezikhathi ezithile kubantu abaxhumana nabo eduze abikwe emazweni ahlukahlukene aseYurophu naseTunisia.
Okunye ukuqubuka kwesibili kwenzeka eNingizimu Korea ngo-2015 ngezigameko eziqinisekisiwe ezingu-186.
