Noma kunjalo, izici ze-SARS-CoV-2 ezihlanganisa ukutheleleka kwayo, ukutheleleka nokusabalala okuqhubekayo ngemuva kokudlula kubantu kuzoba nomthelela ekugcineni kokuqubuka okuqhubekayo kwe-COVID-19.
Wonke ama-HCV amane atholakala emphakathini abangela izimpawu ezincane asezivumelanise kahle nabantu.
