Kudingeka zigcine futhi zisakaze ezindaweni zazo ze-zoonotic futhi zifune ithuba lokudlulela eziqondisweni zabantu ezizwelayo, mhlawumbe ngokusebenzisa isilwane esisodwa noma eziningi eziphakathi nokukhulisa.
I-SARS-CoV-2 inezici ezifanayo kuzo zombili i-SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV kanye nama-HCoV amane atholakala emphakathini.
Iyakwazi ukudluliseka kakhulu njenge-HCoVs etholakala emphakathini, okungenani okwamanje.
Kodwa-ke, i-pathogenic kakhulu kune-HCoVs etholwe umphakathi futhi ayisiyingozi kangako kune-SARS-CoV noma i-MERS-CoV.
Kusazobonakala ukuthi ingabe iyokwazi yini ukuzivumelanisa ngokugcwele nabantu futhi isakaze phakathi kwabantu ngaphandle kwesilwane esiyisisekelo noma esiphakathi.
Ngaphambi kokuxoxa ngemvelaphi yezilwane yama-HCV, kuzosisiza ukuxoxa ngezincazelo kanye nezici ze-evolutionary, natural, reservoir, intermediate kanye ne-amplifying hosts yama-HCV.
Isilwane sisebenza njengomphathi wokuziphendukela kwemvelo we-HCoV uma sihlala nokhokho ohlobene kakhulu owabelana ngokufana okuphezulu ezingeni le-nucleotide sequence.
