Ngokufanayo, umnikazi wesigcine uhlala ne-HCoV ngokuqhubekayo nangesikhathi eside.
Kuzo zombili lezi zimo, izibukeli zitheleleka ngokwemvelo futhi zingabameli bemvelo be-HCoV noma igciwane labazali bayo.
Ngokuphambene, uma i-HCoV isanda kungeniswa kumgcini ophakathi ngaphambi noma ngaphambi nje kokungeniswa kwayo kubantu, ayivumelani kahle nomgcini omusha futhi ivame ukuba ne-pathogenic.
Lo mphathi ophakathi nendawo angasebenza njengomthombo we-zoonosis wokutheleleka kwabantu futhi adlale indima yokuba ngumgcini oqinisa ngokwenza igciwane likwazi ukuphindaphindeka okwesikhashana bese lilidlulisela kubantu ukuze likhulise izinga lokutheleleka kwabantu.
I-HCoV ingase ihlasele uma ingakwazi ukuqhubeka nokudluliswa kwayo ngaphakathi kwesiguli esiphakathi.
Ngokuphambene nalokho, ama-HCV nawo angakwazi ukuzivumelanisa nomgcini ophakathi nendawo futhi aze asungule ubukhona besikhathi eside.
Kulokhu, isilwane esiphakathi siba isilwane esihlala endaweni yemvelo.
Imininingwane ye-epidemiological yaveza ukuthi isigameko esiyisihluthulelo se-SARS sasinomlando wokuxhumana nezilwane ezizingelwayo.
Ucwaningo olwalwenziwa kamuva lokutholakala kwe-seroprevalence lwabonisa ukuthi abathengisi bezilwane babenokusakazeka okuphezulu kwe-anti-SARS-CoV IgG uma kuqhathaniswa naleyo yabantu abavamile.
