Lokhu kwaxhaswa ngokungaqondile yiqiniso lokuthi akuzange kubikwe okunye ukuhlaselwa yi-SARS ngemva kokubulawa kwazo zonke izimpungushe ezimakethe.
Kodwa-ke, kubikwe ukuthi ama-civet asezindaweni zasendle noma emapulazini angathintwanga izimakethe zezilwane eziphilayo ayevame ukungabi nawo umthelela ku-SARS-CoV, okusikisela ukuthi ama-civet asezindaweni zasendle angase asebenze kuphela njengenduna ephakathi yokukhulisa kodwa hhayi indawo yemvelo ye-SARS-CoV.
