Ama-CoV afana ne-SARS (SL-CoVs) amaningana nawo aye atholakala kubelulwane, kodwa akukho ngaphandle kwe-WIV1 eyodwa engahlukaniswa njengegciwane eliphilayo.
I-human angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) yaziwa njengama-receptor e-SARS-CoV.
I-WIV1 ethathwe esibonelweni sobulungu bamabhakede amabhakede yaboniswa ukuthi isebenzisa i-bat, i-civet ne-ACE2 yomuntu njenge-receptor yokungena kwamaseli.
Ngokuthakazelisayo, ama-serum eziguli ze-SARS ezazisaphila ayakwazi ukuvimbela i-WIV1.
Kuze kube manje, i-WIV1 imele ukhokho ohlobene kakhulu we-SARS-CoV kumalulwane, ehlanganyela ama-95% we-homology ye-nucleotide sequence.
Nakuba kunokufana okuphezulu phakathi kwalezi zinhlobo ezimbili zamagciwane, kuvame ukukholelwa ukuthi i-WIV1 akuyona igciwane lomzali eliqondile le-SARS-CoV futhi amalulwane akuwona umnikazi wendawo yokugcina we-SARS-CoV.
Ukuhlaziywa kwe-phylogenetic kuhlanganisa i-MERS-CoV neqembu elifanayo ne-bat CoV-HKU4 ne-bat CoV-HKU5.
I-Bat CoV-HKU4 ne-MERS-CoV zisebenzisa i-host receptor efanayo, i-dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4), ukuze igciwane lingene.
Izinhlu ze-RNA polymerase ezincike ku-RNA ze-MERS-CoV ziseduze ngokwemvelaphi yezinhlobo zazo ezifanayo kuma-beta-CoV ama-bat atholakala eYurophu nase-Afrika.
Kuze kube manje, awekho ama-MERS-CoV aphilayo atholakala kumalulwane asendle.
I-MERS-CoV nesihlobo sayo esiseduze i-bat CoV-HKU25 zihlanganisa kuphela i-87% ye-nucleotide sequence homology.
Ngakho, amalulwane kungenzeka angabi yiwona aphatha i-MERS-CoV ngokushesha.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, ucwaningo eMpumalanga Ephakathi lubonise ukuthi amakamela ama-dromedary ane-seropositive for MERS-CoV-specific neutralizing antibodies, njengamakamela aseMpumalanga Ephakathi emazweni amaningi ase-Afrika.
I-MERS-CoV ephilayo efana negciwane elitholakala kubantu yatholakala kuma-nasal swabs amakamela ama-dromedary, okukhombisa ukuthi amakamela ayi-bona fide reservoir host ye-MERS-CoV.
Kuyaphawuleka futhi ukuthi izimpawu ezivamile zingezinhle kodwa ukuchitheka okukhulu kwegciwane kwabonwa kumakamela atheleleke nge-MERS-CoV.
Ikakhulukazi, amakamela anegciwane awachitheki nje kuphela ngemizila yokuphefumula kodwa futhi nangendlela yokuhlanza indle ngomlomo, okuyiyona ndlela eyinhloko yokuchitheka kwegciwane ngamalulwane.
Kodwa-ke, kusasele imibuzo ngoba amacala amaningi aqinisekisiwe e-MERS awanawo umlando wokuxhumana namakamela ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu, okungenzeka ukuthi kungenxa yokudluliselwa komuntu komunye umuntu noma izindlela zokudlulisela ezingaziwa ezibandakanya izinhlobo zezilwane ezingaziwa eziphethe i-MERS-CoV.
I-SARS-CoV-2 ihlanganyela ne-homology ye-nucleotide engu-96.2% ne-bat CoV RaTG13 ehlukaniswe ne-Rhinolophus affinis bats.
Njengasezimeni ze-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, ukwehluka kwe-sequence phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 kukhulu kakhulu ukuthi kungahlukaniswa ubudlelwane bomzali.
Okusho ukuthi, amalulwane kungenzeka angabi yiwona aphethe i-SARS-CoV-2 ngaphandle uma ama-bat CoVs acishe afane atholakala esikhathini esizayo.
Cishe, izilwane eziphakathi eziphethe i-SARS-CoV-2 kufanele zibe phakathi kwezinhlobo zezilwane zasendle ezithengiswayo futhi zibulawe e-Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market, lapho amacala amaningi okuqala e-COVID-19 ayehlotshaniswa khona, okubonisa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi isilwane singena kumuntu.
Ucwaningo olusha olusekelwe ekuhleleni i-metagenomic luye lwaveza ukuthi iqembu lezilwane ezincanyana ezincelisayo ezisengozini eyaziwa ngokuthi ama-pangolin (Manis javanica) nalo lingase libe nama-beta-CoVs okhokho ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lezi zinoveli ze-pangolin CoV genomes zihlanganyela ama-85-92% we-nucleotide sequence homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nokho, zihlobene eduze ne- RaTG13 cishe ngo- 90% ezingeni le- nucleotide sequence.
Zihlanganiswa zibe yizigaba ezimbili zama-virus afana ne-SARS-CoV-2 esihlahleni se-phylogenetic, enye yazo ihlanganyela i-receptor binding domain (RBD) efanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2, enobunye be-amino acid sequence obungu-97.4%.
Ngokuphambene, ama-RBD e-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahluke kakhulu, yize izinga eliphezulu lokulandelana kwe-homology genome-wide.
Ucwaningo lwangaphambilini olwenziwe kuma-pangolin agulayo luphinde lwabika ngokutholakala kwama-contigs egciwane kumasampula omphimbo, okuvela ukuthi ahlobene ngokufanayo ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Lolu cwaningo lwasebenzisa izindlela zokuhlanganisa ezahlukene kanye nokulinganisa ngesandla ukuze kukhiqizwe ukulandelana kwe-genome okuyingxenye okuhlanganisa cishe u-86.3% we-genome egcwele yegciwane.
Asikwazi ukulahla ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi i-pangolin ingenye yezilwane eziphakathi ezihlala i-SARS-CoV-2.
Kodwa-ke, okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obusekela ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ivela ngokuqondile emhlanjeni ngenxa yokwehluka ngokulandelana phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kanye nama-beta-CoVs ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 emhlanjeni.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ibanga phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 lilifushane ngisho naphakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-beta-CoVs ye-pangolin ehlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Indlela yokuziphendukela kwemvelo ye-SARS-CoV-2 kumalulwane, ama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusafanele isungulwe.
Nakuba ukulandelana okuphezulu kakhulu kutholakale kuma-RBDs phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-pangolin, ama-beta-CoV ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, i-SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ahlanganyela ukulandelana okuphezulu kakhulu kwe-genome-wide.
Kucatshangwa kakhulu ukuthi ukufana okuphezulu phakathi kwama-RBDs we-pangolin SARS-CoV-2-related beta-CoVs kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 kuqhutshwa ukuguquguquka okuguquguqukayo okuxhaswe ngokukhetha.
Isiphakamiso esiphikisayo sivumelana nokuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kwe-beta-CoV ehlobene ne-pangolin SARS-CoV-2 ne-RaTG13 ezinhlotsheni zezilwane zasendle zesithathu.
Njengamandla ashukumisayo ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwandile phakathi kwama-beta-CoV.
Iqembu labaphenyi lisaqhubeka nokuphikisana ngemvelaphi esheshayo ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Ngaphandle kwama-HCoV anobuthi obuphezulu, imvelaphi ye-zoonotic ye-HCoV-229E, i-HCoV-OC43, i-HCoV-NL63 kanye ne-HCoV-HKU1 nayo iye yafundwa.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bukhombisa ukuthi bobabili i-HCoV-NL63 ne-HCoV-229E kungenzeka ukuthi zivela kuma-bat CoVs, kanti amagciwane omzali we-HCoV-OC43 ne-HCoV-HKU1 atholakale ezinambuzaneni.
