I-MERS-CoV iyisibonelo esihle kakhulu sokudluliselwa kwezilwane ezifuywayo kusuka kumalulwane kuya kumakamela ase-dromedary kanye nokusuka kumakamela ase-dromedary kuya kubantu.
Umsuka wokuziphendukela kwemvelo we-MERS-CoV ovela kumalulwane waziwa ngesikhathi sokuhlonza kwawo kokuqala futhi futhi kwaqiniswa okutholakele kamuva.
Kusobala ukuthi amalulwane anikeza inqwaba yezinhlobo zamagciwane okushintshaniswa kwezingxenye zofuzo phakathi kwezinhlobo nokudluliselwa kwazo phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ukuphila isikhathi eside, imiphakathi eminyene, ukuxhumana nabantu kanye nekhono eliqinile lokundiza konke kuyisimo esihle sokuba amalulwane abe 'abasabalalisi begciwane' abahle.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, sekungamashumi eminyaka i-MERS-CoV ingeniswa emakameleni ama-dromedary.
Ivumelane kahle nalamakamela asuke ekubeni umsizi wesikhashana abe umsizi ozinzile nongokwemvelo.
I-MERS-CoV ibangela isifo esincane kakhulu futhi igcina izinga lokuziphendukela kwemvelo liphansi kulezi zilwane.
Ukutheleleka kwayo kubantu ngezikhathi ezithile kuyingozi futhi abantu bahlala bengabaphathi be-MERS-CoV njengoba ukutheleleka kwayo kungeke kuqhubeke.
Ngokuphambene nendima yamakamela ekusakazeni i-MERS-CoV, indima yama-pangolin, uma ikhona, ekusakazeni i-SARS-CoV-2 yehlukile.
Ikakhulu, ama-beta-CoV ama-pangolin ayingozi kakhulu kuma-pangolin.
Kungenzeka kube yizihlobo ezifile zama-beta-CoV ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2, afana nama-civet e-SARS-CoV.
Amathuba amaningi okuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 isakazeke phakathi kwezinhlobo ezithile isuka ezilwaneni iye kubantu kufanele ashiywe ngaphandle noma agwenywe ezifundweni ezizayo.
Okokuqala, amalulwane angaba yizindawo ezigcina igciwane elihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 elicishe lifane ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Abantu bangase bahlanganyele indawo yemvelo namalulwane ngokubulala noma ngokumba amalahle.
Okwesibili, ama-pangolin angaba ngomunye wabasakazi abaphakathi lapho i-SARS-CoV-2 i-virus ehlobene nayo isanda kungeniswa khona.
Abantu bathola igciwane ngokuhlakaza nangokudla inyama yezilwane.
Kungenzeka ukuthi izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane ezifuywayo ziyathinteka ku-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuhlolwa kwezilwane ezifuyiwe nezingeyomvelo ukuze kutholakale ama-antibody kuyadingeka.
Okwesithathu, njengoba kushiwo ngenhla, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha nokuzivumelanisa kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kungenzeka ukuthi kwenzeke ezinhlotsheni ezintathu ezithintana namalulwane nama-pangolin.
Ukufuna imvelaphi yezilwane ye-SARS-CoV-2 kusaqhubeka.
Ngaphandle kwezinhlobo ezahlukene zezilwane ezihlala kuzo, izici ezintathu ezinkulu ezingasohlangothini lwegciwane nazo zibalulekile ekulungiseleleni ama-Cov ukuze adlule izithiyo zezinhlobo.
Okokuqala, amazinga abo okuguquka okuphakeme kakhulu ekuziphindiseleni kwe-RNA.
Uma kuqhathaniswa namanye amagciwane e-RNA ane-stranded eyodwa, izinga lokuhlukahluka elilinganisiwe lama-CoV lingabhekwa njenge-  eliphakathi  kuya ku-  eliphakeme  ngesilinganiso sokushintshana okuphakathi kuka- ~ 10-4 ngonyaka endaweni 2, kuye ngesigaba sokuzivumelanisa kwe-CoV ne- novel hosts.
Ama-Covid ane-exoribonuclease yokuhlola, ukususwa kwayo okuholela ekutheni kube nokuguquka okuphezulu kakhulu nokunciphisa noma ngisho nokungaphili.
Kuyathakazelisa ukuthi i-nucleotide analogue Remdesivir yaziwa ngokucindezela ukuphindaphinda kwe-CoV ngokuvimbela le exoribonuclease kanye ne-RNA polymerase ethembele ku-RNA.
I-remdesivir ingenye yezindlela ezithembisa kakhulu zokulwa ne-SARS-CoV-2 ezizohlolwa ezivivinyweni zomtholampilo.
Noma kunjalo, amazinga okuguquka kwama-CoV aphakeme ngokuphindwe izikhathi ezicishe zibe yisigidi kunalawo ama-CoV aphikisana nawo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga lokuziphendukela kwemvelo livame ukuba phezulu uma ama-Covid engazivumelanisi kahle nomzimba.
Uma kuqhathaniswa ne-SARS-CoV enesilinganiso esiphezulu sokuguquka, isilinganiso sokuguquka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ngokusobala siphansi, okusikisela izinga eliphakeme lokuzivumelanisa nabantu.
Cishe, kakade sesiye sazivumelanisa nomunye umnikazi oseduze nabantu.
Ngaphezu kwe-SARS-CoV-2, lokhu kusebenza naku-MERS-CoV, okuyiyona evumelana kahle namakamela.
Ngokombono, akunakwenzeka ukuthi ukuguquguquka kwezakhi zofuzo kungenza imithi yokugoma nemithi elwa namagciwane ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2 ingasebenzi ngokushesha.
Okwesibili, i-RNA genome enkulu kuma-CoV inamandla okuthambisa ngokweqile ekuguqulweni kwe-genome ukuze kuguquke futhi kuphinde kuhlanganiswe, ngaleyo ndlela kukhulise amathuba okuthi kuvele ukuziphendukela kwemvelo phakathi kwezinhlobo, okuyinto enenzuzo ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha lapho izimo ziba ezifanele.
Lokhu kusekelwa yizinhlaka zokufunda ezivulekile eziyingqayizivele nemisebenzi yamaprotheni ehlanganiswe ngasekupheleni kwe- 3 ' ye-genome.
Okwesithathu, ama-CoV ashintsha ama-template ngokungahleliwe futhi kaningi ngesikhathi sokuziphindaphinda kwe-RNA ngokusebenzisa indlela eyingqayizivele ye-copy-choice.
Kumuntu osebenza njengesitsha sokuxuba, ukushintshana kwe-strand kwenzeka kaningi ngesikhathi sokubhalwa kwe-RNA ye-Cov.
Ama-RNA anobude obuphelele obufanayo kakhulu kanye nama-RNA angaphansi kwe-genomic angahlanganiswa kabusha ukuze akhiqize ama-CoV amasha.
Ubufakazi be-phylogenetic bokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwemvelo butholakale kokubili ku-HCoV-HKU1 naku-HCoV-OC43, kanye nama-CoV ezilwane afana ne-bat SL-CoV ne-batCoV-HKU9.
Ukusebenzelana kwegciwane nomgcini maqondana nokudluliselwa
Ngaphandle kwalezi zinto ezintathu ezibangelwa amagciwane ezichazwe ngenhla, ukusebenzelana kwegciwane ne-host receptor kungenye into ebalulekile ethinta ukudluliselwa kwe-interspecies.
Lapha, ukuhlanganiswa kabusha kwe-SARS-CoV kuthathwa njengesibonelo esivamile, okubuye kwabonisa ubufakazi bokukhethwa okuhle ngesikhathi sezenzakalo zokudluliswa kwe-interspecies.
Ngokusekelwe ekuhlaziyweni kokuqhathanisa phakathi kwe-SARS-CoVs yabantu nezilwane ezifuywayo, i-SARS-CoV kucatshangwa ukuthi ivumelana nezimo ngokushesha kumamukeli ahlukene, ikakhulukazi ngokuvela kwe-RBD yeprotheni ye-S.
Ngokuvamile, i-RBD ku-S protein ye-Covid ihlangana ne-cell receptor futhi ikhethwa ngamandla impendulo ye-antibody yomnikazi.
Ku-SARS-CoV, i-RBD isendaweni engu-318 kuya ku-510 kuma-amino acid ku-S1 fragment, ebopha i-ACE2 yomuntu kanye nama-coreceptors ayo ukuze igciwane lingene.
I-RBD ye-SARS-CoV iyakwazi ukubona ama-ACE2 receptors ezilwaneni ezihlukahlukene, kuhlanganise namalulwane, ama-civet, amagundane kanye nezinja ezi-raccoon, okuvumela ukudluliselwa kwegciwane phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Eqinisweni, kwatholakala ukuthi ama-amino acid angu-6 kuphela ahlukile kuma-virus abantu kanye nama-civet e-RBD futhi angu-4 awo atholakala ku-receptor-binding motif ukuze asebenzelane ne-ACE2 receptor.
I-Civet SARS-CoV inezinguquko ze-K479N ne-S487T ku-RBD yayo, okungase kwandise ukuhlobana kokusebenzisana kwe-spike protein ne-human ACE2 receptor.
Ngamanye amazwi, lezi zinguquko ezimbili zama-amino acid zingase zibe nethonya elikhulu ekuzivumelaniseni kwamagciwane nabantu.
Kuyaphawuleka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 inemibhobho efanayo ne-SARS-CoV.
Umehluko ongu-30% phakathi kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ne-SARS-CoV kuyunithi le-S1 le-protein ye-S kusho ukuthi ukuhlobana kokubopha kwe-protein yayo ye-S ne-ACE2 yomuntu kungenzeka ukuthi kuguqukile.
Ngempela, ucwaningo lwe-cryo-EM lubonisa ukuthi lokhu kuhlangana kunamandla aphindwe izikhathi ezingu-10 kuya kwezingu-20 kunalokho okuphakathi kwe-ACE2 yomuntu ne-SARS-CoV S protein.
Kuyoba nentshisekelo futhi ukuthola ukuthi ngabe kukhona yini amanye ama-coreceptor angadingeka ukuze kudluliswe i-SARS-CoV-2.
Okuphawulekayo ukuthi i-HCoV-NL63 nayo ibopha i-ACE2 kodwa ngezingxenye ezahlukene ze-S.
Kukhona amanye ama-receptor amaningi e-HCoV, njenge-aminopeptidase N ye-HCoV-229E, ne-9-O-acetylated sialic acid ye-HCoV-OC43.
Kungenzeka futhi kube yibo ababhekene nokuzivumelanisa ngempumelelo kwalezi CoVs kubantu ngemuva kokudluliselwa kwezinhlobo ezivela ezilwaneni ezizifuyile.
Ngaphezu kwama-cell receptors, umphumela wokudluliswa kwama-HCoVs phakathi kwezinhlobo nawo ulawulwa okunye ukuncika komnikazi kanye nezici zokuvimbela.
Ukuhlukahluka kwalamaphrotheni omzimba phakathi kwabantu kanye nama-HCoVs emvelo afana namalulwane, amakamela ama-dromedary kanye namagundane kungase kubangele ukuba kungabikho ukusakazeka phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Ama-HCoV kufanele athathe izakhi zokuncika kumgcini futhi aphule izakhi zokuvimbela umnikazi ukuze adluliselwe ngempumelelo phakathi kwezinhlobo.
Kulokhu, izakhi ezinquma i-molecular kule ndawo ebalulekile yokuxhumana kwegciwane nomzimba kusafanele zikhonjwe futhi zichazwe.
Ukuhlolwa kwe-genome-wide okungenakuphikiswa kokuncika kwe-host kanye nezici zokuvimbela i-SARS-CoV-2 kusetshenziswa ubuchwepheshe bamuva be-CRISPR kungaba nomphumela.
Ukuvela kwama-CoV amasha: emuva endaweni yokuqala
Ukuhlukahluka kwama-Covs ama-bat kunikeza amathuba amaningi okuvela kwama-HCoV amasha.
Ngale ndlela, ama-Covs amadada asebenza njengengxenye ye-gen pool yama-HCoV.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, ukuguquka kwesimo okusheshayo nokuhlanganiswa kabusha kwezakhi zofuzo nakho kuholela ekuziphendukeleni kwemvelo kwe-HCoV futhi kusebenza njengezinyathelo ezimbili ezibalulekile kule nqubo.
Ngokwesibonelo, ukuthola noma ukulahlekelwa ama-protein-coding genes amasha kunamandla okuguqula kakhulu ama-phenotypes amagciwane.
Phakathi kwamaprotheni aseceleni e-SARS-CoV, i-ORF8 kucatshangwa ukuthi ibalulekile ekuzivumelaniseni nabantu, njengoba amagciwane amalulwane ahlobene ne-SARS-CoV ahlukaniswa kodwa atholakala ukuthi afaka amaprotheni e-ORF8 ahlukene.
Ukususwa kwe-nucleotide okungu-29 okuyisici sama-SARS-CoVs kutholakale ezinhlotsheni ezihlukanisiwe ekuqaleni kwalolu bhubhane kubantu.
Lokhu kususwa kuhlukanisa i-ORF8 ibe i-ORF8a ne-ORF8b futhi kucatshangwa ukuthi kuyinguquko eguquguqukayo ekhuthaza ukushintshwa kwama-hosts.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, i-SARS-CoV inomlando wokuphinda uhlangane nama-alpha- kanye nama-gamma-CoV, lapho kutholakale khona inani elikhulu lezifunda ezincane eziphinda zihlangane ku-RNA-dependent RNA polymerase.
Izindawo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha nazo zabonwa ku-nsp9, iningi le-nsp10, kanye nezingxenye ze-nsp14.
Ngokufanayo, kuboniswe ukuthi ubhubhane lwe-MERS-CoV lwabhekana nezimo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha phakathi kohlu lozalo oluhlukile, okwenzeka emakameleni e-Saudi Arabia.
Ngaphandle kwe-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV, izenzakalo zokuhlanganiswa kabusha ziye zabonwa nakweminye i-HCVs, lapho i-HCVs ihlangana kabusha namanye ama-CoVs ezilwane kumagene awo angekho ngokwakhiwa.
Kufanele futhi kuqaphelwe ukuthi ukukhetha okufakelwa kungasiza ekwenzeni izinguquko ezingahlosiwe kuma-virus genomes, okungenzeka kakhulu ukuthi kubangelwa ukukhulula amagciwane ekucindezelweni kokukhetha, njengokusetshenziswa kwesimiso somzimba somzimba.
Isibonelo salokhu imiphumela ukulahleka kwe-ORF4 ephelele kuhlobo lwe-HCoV-229E prototype, ngenxa yokususwa kwama-nucleotide amabili.
Ngenkathi i-ORF4 engaguquki ibonakala kuma-virus wamalulwane namakamela ahlobene ne-HCoV-229E, i-alpaca alpha-CoV ibonisa ukufakwa kwe-nucleotide eyodwa, okuholela ekushintsheni kwesakhiwo.
Okokugcina, ukuvela kwama-HCoV amasha nakho kuqhutshwa ukucindezela kokukhetha kumnikazi wawo wendawo.
Izimpawu ezingenazimpawu noma ezincane kuphela zabonwa lapho amalulwane etheleleke nge-CovVs, okukhombisa ukuzivumelanisa okuhambisanayo phakathi kwe-CovVs nama-bat.
Kwabonakala ukuthi amalulwane azivumelanisa kahle nama-CoV ngokwemizimba nangokomzimba.
Isibonelo, amaphutha ekuvuseleleni impendulo evuselela ukuvuvukala emagqabeni anciphisa ngokuphumelelayo i-pathology ebangwa yi-CoVs.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, umsebenzi wamangqamuzana ombulali wemvelo kumalulwane ucindezelwa ngenxa yokwanda kokulawulwa kwe-receptor ye-NKG2/CD94 yamangqamuzana ombulali wemvelo kanye nezinga eliphansi lokuveza ama-molecule amakhulu e-class I.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, izinga eliphakeme lezinhlobo zomoya-mpilo ezisebenzayo (ROS) ezikhiqizwa umsebenzi ophakeme we-metabolic wamalulwane zingacindezela ukuphindaphindeka kwe-CoV futhi zithinte ukufundwa kokuhlelwa kwe-exoribonuclease, ngaleyo ndlela zinikeze ingcindezi yokukhetha ukukhiqiza izinhlobo zegciwane elinamandla kakhulu lapho zingeniswa kumsingathi omusha.
Izinhlobo ze- CoV ezinobuthi obukhulu zingase futhi ziguquke ngokuhlanganiswa kabusha, okuholele ekutholeni amaprotheni amasha noma izici zamaprotheni ukuze zilungele ukujwayela umnikazi.
Ngakho-ke, akukhona ngengozi ukuthi ama-HCoV amathathu amasha avele emashumini amabili eminyaka adlule.
Ama-CoV awawona ama-pathogenic noma abangela izimpawu ezincane kumagceke awo afana namalulwane namakamela.
Ziziphindaphinda ngokuqinile ngaphandle kokubangela ukuphendula okuqinile komzimba.
Yilapha lapho izimfihlo zokuthi kungani kubonakala abathwali abangenazo izimpawu nokuthi yini ebangela izifo ezinzima kubantu.
Izimpawu ezinzima zibangelwa kakhulu ukuvuselelwa kwempendulo yomzimba kanye nesiphepho se-cytokine lapho impendulo yomzimba enamandla kakhulu, umonakalo wamaphaphu unzima kakhulu.
Ngokuphambene, kubathwali abangenazimpawu, impendulo yomzimba yokuzivikela komzimba iye yahlukaniswa nokuziphindaphinda kwe-CoV.
Isu elifanayo lokuhlukanisa impendulo yamasosha omzimba lingaba nemiphumela ezuzisayo ekwelashweni kwe-anti-SARS-CoV-2.
Impendulo ye-interferon inamandla kakhulu kumalulwane.
Ngakho, ukunikezwa kwe-interferon yohlobo I okungenani esigabeni sokuqala sokutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 kubantu kufanele kube wusizo.
Ngaphezu kwalokho, i-NLRP3 inflammasome activation kumalulwane ayilungile.
Ngalesi sizathu, ukuvinjelwa kwe-NLRP3 inflammasome nge-MCC950 kungase kube wusizo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Ukuvela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 kulandela isihloko esivamile okuvela ngaso i-SARS-CoV ne-MERS-CoV.
Nakuba kutholakale i-beta-CoV yamalulwane ehlanganyela ama-95% we-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV, kukhona futhi i-bat-CoV ehlanganyela ama-96% we-nucleotide homology ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kutholakale ukuthi izilwane ezifuywayo kanye nezinye izilwane ezimakethe zinegciwane elifana ne-SARS-CoV, izilwane ezifuywayo eziphakathi ezihlobene ne-SARS-CoV-2 azikaze zitholakale.
Kutholakale ama-beta-CoV e-pangolin ahlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2, okukhombisa ukuthi ama-pangolin angaba ngomunye wezivakashi eziphakathi noma ama-beta-CoV e-pangolin anganikela ngezingcezu ze-gene enguqulweni yokugcina ye-SARS-CoV-2.
Nakuba kusekhona imibuzo, abukho ubufakazi bokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 yenziwe umuntu ngamabomu noma ngengozi.
Ama-Cov abuyele endaweni yesikhalazo ngenxa yokuqubuka kwe-SARS-CoV-2 muva nje.
Ucwaningo lwe-Covs kuma-bat nezinye izilwane lushintshe kakhulu umbono wethu ngokubaluleka kwemvelaphi ye-zoonotic kanye nemithombo yezilwane yama-CoVs ekusakazweni kwabantu.
Ubufakazi obukhona bubonisa ukuthi i-SARS-CoV, i-MERS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zivela emabhakedeni futhi zidluliselwa kubantu ngokusebenzisa izilwane eziphakathi.
Njengoba ukutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV kuvela ekuthintaneni kwabantu nezinyoni ezimakethe, ukuvala izimakethe ezimanzi nokubulala izinyoni kuzo bekungaqeda ubhubhane lwe-SARS.
Ngesizathu esifanayo, ama-pangolin kufanele asuswe ezimakethe ezimanzi ukuze kuvinjelwe ukudluliselwa kwe-zootic, ngenxa yokutholakala kwemigqa eminingi yama-pangolin beta-CoVs ahlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Kodwa-ke, ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 idluliselwa kanjani kubantu ngama-pangolin nezinye izilwane ezincelisayo kusazodingeka kucaciswe uphenyo lwesikhathi esizayo.
Ngakolunye uhlangothi, i-MERS-CoV ibilokhu ikhona ezinkameleni ezincelisayo isikhathi eside.
La makamela ayithuluzi elibalulekile kwezokuhamba futhi awumthombo oyinhloko wenyama, ubisi, isikhumba nemikhiqizo yoboya kubantu bendawo.
Zisakazeke kabanzi eMpumalanga Ephakathi nase-Afrika.
Ngakho-ke akunakwenzeka ukunikela ngawo wonke amakamela ukuze kulawulwe i-MERS, njengoba kwenziwa ezimakethe zezilwane zasendle eChina ukuvimbela ukusabalala kwe-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Ukuze kunqandwe ukuqubuka okuphindaphindiwe kwe-MERS, kufanele kuthathwe indlela ephelele yokuthuthukisa imishanguzo esebenzayo yokulwa ne-MERS-CoV yamakamela, ngokuhlanganiswa nezinye izindlela zokulawula ukutheleleka.
Njengoba singakwazi ukuwaqeda la magciwane, kungase kuvele izinhlobo ezintsha zofuzo ezibangela ukuqubuka kwezifo.
Izinhlobonhlobo zama-CoV ezibangelwa abantu ziyavela futhi ziyasakazeka endle.
Ikakhulukazi, ama-CoV amaphiko ane-zoonotic potential ahlukahlukene kakhulu.
Kunamathuba amaningi okuthi la ma-CoVs avela ezilwaneni aguquke futhi ahlangane, okuholele ekuveleni kwama-CoV amasha adluliseleka kakhulu futhi/noma abulalayo kubantu esikhathini esizayo.
Isiko lokudla izilwane zasendle kwezinye izindawo zaseChina kufanele lilahlwe ukuze kuncishiswe ukuxhumana okungadingekile phakathi kwabantu nezilwane.
Ngenxa yezinhlupheko ze-SARS, i-MERS ne-COVID-19, kufanele kube khona ukulungela okungcono kanye nohlelo lokuphendula.
Eqinisweni, amagciwane amaningi abelokhu ekhona emhlabeni isikhathi eside kakhulu.
Zihlala ezindaweni zazo zemvelo kuze kube yilapho sekunethuba lokudlulela.
Nakuba amalulwane enezici eziningi ezenza kube lula ukusakazeka kwama-virus, amathuba okuba abantu baxhumane nawo kanye nezinye izilwane zasendle angancishiswa uma abantu befundiswa ukuba bangaxhumani nawo.
Ukuqapha okuqhubekayo kwezilwane ezincelisayo kuyadingeka ukuze kuqondwe kangcono isimo se-CovV nezilwane ezihlala kuzo, okuzoba wusizo ekuvimbeleni ukudluliselwa kwegciwane lisuka esilwaneni liya kubantu nokuqubuka esikhathini esizayo.
Ekuphetheni, indlela ephumelela kunazo zonke yokuvimbela i-virus zoonosis iwukuba abantu bahlale kude nezindawo zemvelo zama-virus ezi-zoonotic.
Izingcezu eziningana zephazili yemvelaphi ye-zoonotic ye-SARS-CoV-2 zisanyamalala.
Okokuqala, uma amalulwane edlulisela igciwane lozalo lwe-SARS-CoV-2 kuma-pangolin, kuyoba okuthakazelisayo ukubona ukuthi ngaphansi kwaziphi izimo amalulwane nama-pangolin angabelana nge-niche efanayo yemvelo.
Okwesibili, uma amalulwane edlala indima eqondile ekusakazeni isifo kubantu, kufanele kunqunywe ukuthi abantu bangena kanjani kula malulwane.
Okwesithathu, uma isilwane sesithathu esincelisayo sisebenza njengesilwane esiphakathi, indlela esisebenzelana ngayo nezinhlobo ezahlukene kuhlanganise nabantu, amalulwane nama-pangolin kufanele kucaciswe.
Okokugcina, njengoba izilwane eziningi ezincelisayo kuhlanganise nezilwane ezifuywayo zingase zibhekane ne-SARS-CoV-2, kokubili ukuqapha nokutheleleka kokuhlola kufanele kwenziwe.
Uma ngabe kungumkhovuzi, i-pangolin noma esinye isilwane esincelisayo, kulindeleke ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 noma amagciwane ayo omzali acishe afane nawo azotholakala kumakhosikazi ayo emvelo esikhathini esizayo.
Ucwaningo oluqhubekayo kule ndawo luzokhanyisa indlela yokuziphendukela kwe-SARS-CoV-2 ezilwaneni, okunemithelela ebalulekile ekuvikeleni nasekulawuleni i-COVID-19 kubantu.
Ukuvuselela imigomo yokuxilonga i-COVID-19  icala elisolisayo kanye ne  icala eliqinisekisiwe kuyadingeka
Ngo-6 Februwari 2020, ithimba lethu lashicilela isiqondiso esisheshayo sokwelulekwa sokuxilongwa nokwelashwa kokutheleleka okusha kwe-coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ka-2019, futhi lesi siqondiso sinikeze ulwazi lwethu futhi senza inkomba enhle yokulwa nalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Kodwa-ke, isifo i-coronavirus 2019 (i-COVID-19) yisifo esisha, ukuqwashisa kwethu nolwazi lwethu lukhula kancane kancane ngokusekelwe emiphumeleni yocwaningo oluqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho kokusebenza kwemitholampilo; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo avuselelwa njalo.
Kule ncwadi, siphendule ukuphawula okukodwa mayelana nesikhombisi-ndlela sethu futhi sanikeza izindlela zokuthola izifo zakamuva ze- cases esoliswayo kanye ne- cases eqinisekisiwe ngokusho kwe-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (inguqulo yesikhombisa) yakamuva ekhishwe yi-National Health Committee of the People's Republic of China.
NgoDisemba 2019, i-coronavirus entsha ka-2019 (2019-nCoV) yabangela ukuqubuka, manje ebizwa ngokusemthethweni ngokuthi isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) futhi igciwane labizwa ngokuthi i-severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ngo-March 11, 2020, i-WHO yachaza i-COVID-19 njengobhadane.
Ukuze silwe nokutheleleka kwe-SARS-CoV-2, ithimba lethu lisungule umhlahlandlela wokweluleka ngokushesha futhi osushicilelwe ku-inthanethi ku-Military Medical Research ngomhlaka 06 Febhuwari 2020.
Sekuyithakazelise kakhulu kusukela yashicilelwa.
Nokho, qaphela ukuthi i-COVID-19 yisifo esisha, ukuqwashisa nolwazi lwethu luyanda kancane kancane ngokusekelwe emiphumeleni yocwaningo eqhubekayo kanye nokuhlangenwe nakho kokusebenza kwemitholampilo; ngakho-ke, amasu okuxilonga nokwelashwa nawo avuselelwa ngokuqhubekayo.
Isibonelo, Imihlahlandlela Yokuxilongwa Nokwelashwa kwe-COVID-19 ekhishwe yiKomiti Yezempilo kaZwelonke yasePeople's Republic of China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), phakathi kuka-16 Januwari 2020 kuya ku-3 Mashi 2020, ikhishwe ingqikithi yezinguqulo eziyisikhombisa kanti ezinye izingqikithi zishintshwe kakhulu.
Manje umhlahlandlela wethu uthole ukuphawula kukaZhou et al., baletha isiphakamiso sokulinganisa esilula esuselwa kokuhlangenwe nakho kwabo kokwelashwa.
Umsebenzi wabo wengeze ubufakazi obusha esiqondisweni sethu futhi wenza inkomba ebalulekile yalolu bhubhane emhlabeni wonke.
Siyawusekela umsebenzi wabo obalulekile futhi sibabonga.
Kodwa-ke, umsebenzi wabo udinga ukuvuselelwa ngokuya nge-Diagnosis and Treatment Guidelines for COVID-19 (Trial seventh version) yakamuva kanye nezifundo zakamuva.
Ngokwe-edition yesikhombisa (3 March 2020), ukuqinisekisa ukuthi umuntu osolisayo udinga ukuhlanganisa noma yiliphi iphuzu lezimpawu zomlando wobhubhane kanye namaphuzu amabili okubonakaliswa komtholampilo ukwenza ukuhlaziywa okuphelele, noma udinga ukuhlangabezana namaphuzu amathathu okubonakaliswa komtholampilo uma kungekho umlando obonakalayo wobhubhane:
Umlando wokwelashwa kwegciwane: (1) umlando wokuhamba noma ukuhlala edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma kwezinye izindawo lapho kubikwe khona amacala e-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (2) umlando wokuxhumana namacala athathelwanayo e-SARS-CoV-2 (ngokuhlolwa kwe-nucleic acid okuvumayo); (3) umlando wokuxhumana neziguli ezinomkhuhlane noma izimpawu zokuphefumula ezivela edolobheni laseWuhan nasezindaweni ezizungezile, noma eminye imiphakathi lapho kubikwe khona i-COVID-19 ezinsukwini ezingu-14 ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu; (4) umlando wokuxhumana namaqembu amacala aqinisekisiwe (amacala angaphezu kuka-2 anomkhuhlane noma izimpawu zokuphefumula zenzeka kungakapheli amasonto amabili ezindaweni ezincane, njengekhaya, ehhovisi, ekilasini lesikole, njll.).
Izimpawu zokwelashwa: (1) umkhuhlane kanye/ noma izimpawu zokuphefumula; (2) nezici zokuveza izithombe zokutheleleka nge-COVID-19; (3) inani eliphelele lamangqamuzana amhlophe egazi elibonisa inani elijwayelekile, elinciphayo, noma elincishisiwe lamangqamuzana e-lymph.
Ukuxilonga icala eliqinisekisiwe kufanele kususelwe esimweni esisodwa esisolwayo esinobufakazi obuthile bokuthi siwumkhuhlane noma obuthile obungobuchwepheshe njengokulandelayo: (1) ukuhlolwa kwe-PCR ngesikhathi sangempela kunomphumela omuhle we-SARS-CoV-2; (2) ukulandelana kwe-genome ephelele yegciwane okukhombisa ukufana okuphezulu kuma-coronavirus amasha aziwayo; (3) ukuhlolwa kwe-serum kunomphumela omuhle we-antibody eqondene ne-IgM ne-antibody ye-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2; noma ushintsho lwe-antibody ye-IgG ye-SARS-CoV-2 eqondene ne-negative to positive, noma i-titer ekhuphuka izikhathi ezi-4 esigabeni sokululama kunesesigabeni esibucayi.
Sibona ukuthi isivivinyo se-PCR sesikhathi sangempela se-nucleic acid emigwaqweni yokuphefumula noma amasampula egazi afakwa ohlwini lwesibili (ngoJanuwari 18, 2020) nolwesithathu (ngoJanuwari 22, 2020).
Ukubonwa kwe-pathogenic yesampula legazi kwengezwa kumagazini wesine (27 Januwari 2020) nowesihlanu (8 Februwari 2020); bese kuthi ubufakazi be-serological bengezwe kumagazini wesikhombisa.
Lezi zinguquko zisekelwe emsebenzini wabacwaningi wokufuna ikhithi yokuhlola i-nucleic acid efanelekile ukuze kutholakale ngokushesha, kanye namasampula avela emgudwini wokuphefumula okubandakanya ukuthathwa kwesampula legazi, okwandisa ukutholakala kwamasampula ahlukahlukene, futhi kwasekela ukuletha umphumela omuhle we-antibody othize kumigomo eqinisekisiwe.
Ngaphandle kwalokho, kunobufakazi obandayo obusikhumbuza ukuba siqaphele ngeziguli ezingenazo izimpawu nezingenalo izimpawu.
Ngakho-ke, ishadi lokugeleza likaZhou nabanye. kufanele libuyekezwe, njengoba behlukanisa umuntu ongenazo izimpawu zokwelashwa njengo "ngobungozi obuncane".
Uhlelo lokulinganisa kudingeka futhi luqinisekiswe ekusebenzeni nasekucwaningweni okungeziwe.
Ekuphetheni, sinethemba lokuthi kuzovela ubufakazi obuqondile futhi sicela abafundi ukuba banikeze imibono yabo.
Ukuze kutholakale ukuthi umuntu "usolwa" yini nokuthi "uqinisekisiwe" yini, siphakamisa ukuthi umuntu alandele futhi alalele iziqondiso zakamuva zezwe lakubo.
Ithimba lethu lizobe libuye libuyekeza isiqondiso sethu ukuze sinikeze usizo.
I-Bangladesh ibika ukufa okusha okuyisihlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19, okuyinani eliphakeme kakhulu nsuku zonke
Izolo, iBangladesh iqinisekise ukufa kwabantu abahlanu ngenxa ye-COVID-19 ngosuku.
Lena yinani eliphakeme kakhulu labantu ababulewe yileli gciwane ngosuku.
Kusukela izolo, i-Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Control and Research (IEDCR) yaseBangladesh ibike ukuthi isibalo sabantu ababhalisiwe abanegciwane sihlanganisa abantu abangu-114 abasaphila kanti abangu-33 abasele sebelashwe futhi ababesekhaya.
Sekurekhodwe ukufa kwabantu abangu-17.
Emhlanganweni wezindaba owawuse-inthanethi, umqondisi we-IEDCR, uDkt Meerjady Sabrina Flora, wathi ababulewe babeyizinsizwa ezine kanti owesifazane oyedwa.
Ngokusho kukaDkt Meerjady, ababili babephile iminyaka engaphezu kuka-60, ababili babephakathi kweminyaka engu-51 no-60, kanti omunye wayeneminyaka engu-41 kuya ku-50.
Uthe futhi ababili kulabo ababulewe bangabaseDhaka.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) yamemezela i-COVID-19 njengobhadane ngoMashi 11.
Isikhulu sesibhedlela satshela i-Anatolu Agency, umnyango wezindaba wendawo, ukuthi omunye wabafile kwakunguJalal Saifur Rahman, umqondisi we-Bengali Anti-Corruption Commission, owayethola ukunakekelwa esibhedlela saseKuwait Maitree.
NgoMgqibelo, embikweni wevidiyo ku-inthanethi, uNgqongqoshe Wezokuvakasha kanye namaBridge waseBangladesh u-Obaidul Quader uthe ezokuthutha umphakathi zizovalwa isikhathi eside kunalokho obekuhleliwe ekuqaleni, kuze kube nguMgqibelo ozayo.
Lokhu kuvalwa kwezithuthi zomphakathi ekuqaleni kwaqala ngoMashi 26 futhi kwakuhlelwe ukuthi kuphele ngoMgqibelo, ngo-Ephreli 4.
Ukuhamba kwezinto ezibalulekile - ezokwelapha, uphethiloli nokudla - kwakusavunyelwe.
Amacala okuqala aqoshiwe okutheleleka nge-COVID-19 eBangladesh ngo-Mashi 8, kubantu ababili ababuya e-Italy kanye nomka omunye wabo.
Ngo - March 19, laba abathathu base beye balulama kakade.
I-SARS-CoV-2 idlula abantu abayisigidi abangenwe yizifo emhlabeni wonke
NgoLwesine, inani eliphelele leziguli ezithathelwe i-SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus lidlule isigidi esisodwa emhlabeni wonke, ngokusho kwedatha ye-Johns Hopkins University.
Okungenani abantu abayizinkulungwane ezingama-52 babulawe yi-COVID-19, isifo esibangelwa yi-coronavirus.
Le nqubo yenzeka ngosuku olufanayo neMalawi eyaqinisekisa ngalo izifo zokuqala ze-coronavirus neZambia eyaba nokufa kwayo kokuqala okuhlobene ne-coronavirus.
I-North Korea ithi, kusukela ngoLwesine, ingelinye lamazwe ambalwa asele angenalo igciwane le-coronavirus.
Kuze kube izolo, i-World Health Organization ibike amacala aqinisekisiwe angu-1 051 635, kuhlanganise namacala angu-79 332 emahoreni angamashumi amabili nane ngaphambi kuka-10 ekuseni Isikhathi sase-Central Europe (0800 UTC) ngo-Ephreli 4.
E-United States, kwaqoshwa amacala e-coronavirus angaphezu kwezinkulungwane ezingama-244, ahambisana nokufa kwabantu okungenani abangu-5 900.
I-CBS News ibike, icaphuna idatha ye-Johns Hopkins University, ukuthi kwakunabantu abangaphezu kuka-1 000 e-US ngoLwesithathu ngenxa yokutheleleka nge-coronavirus.
Emhlabeni wonke, amazwe amemezela izindlela eziqinile zokuvimbela lesi sifo ukuba singasakazeki.
NgoLwesine, uSergei Sobyanin, usodolobha waseMoscow, wandisa isikhathi sokuvalwa kwedolobha kuze kube ngo-May 1.
Kuwo wonke amazwe, uMongameli uVladimir Putin wamemezela ukuthi abantu baseRussia bazoqhubeka behola imali ngaphandle kokuya emsebenzini kuze kube ngo - April 30.
IPhalamende lasePortugal lavota ukwelula isimo esibucayi sikazwelonke ngezinsuku ezingu-15; ukuvota kwadluliselwa ngamavoti angu-215 avumayo, kwabanqikaza ukuvota abayishumi, kanye nevoti elilodwa eliphikisayo.
ISaudi Arabia yandisa isikhathi sokufika ekhaya emadolobheni angcwele aseMecca naseMedina ukuze ihlale usuku lonke; ngaphambili, isikhathi sokufika ekhaya sasisebenza kuphela phakathi kuka-3 ntambama no-6 ekuseni.
I-Thailand ihlele ukusebenzisa isikhathi sokufika ekhaya phakathi kuka-10 p.m. no-4 a.m.
Umbusi wase-Ohio, uMike DeWine, wamemezela ukuthi umbuso wawulwelé umyalo wokuba abantu bahlale emakhaya kuze kube uMeyi 1.
Izitolo e-Australia ziyanciphisa imikhawulo yephepha langasese ngokuthenga ngakunye
NgeSonto nangoMgqibelo kusihlwa, izitolo zase-Australia i-Woolworths ne-Coles zehlise imikhawulo yazo yokuthenga iphepha langasese yaba ngamaphakethe amabili nelinye lokuthenga esitolo ngasinye ezitolo zonke ezingeni likazwelonke, ngokulandelana.
I-ALDI nayo yafaka umkhawulo wephakethe elilodwa, ngoMsombuluko.
Le mikhawulo yathunyelwa njengemiyalezo emabhokisini okuthenga, nasemakhasini e-Facebook amaketanga.
Abathengi kuthiwa babeqoqa izimpahla ngenxa yokwesaba i-COVID-19 uma kwenzeka abantu kudingeka bazihlukanise.
NgoLwesithathu, iWoolworths nayo yanciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese ukuze lihanjiswe ekhaya libe yiphakethe elilodwa nge-oda ngalinye.
Lezi zinguquko zilandele umbandela wokubopha ama-pack amane wokuthengiselana owethulwe yiWoolworths noColes ngoMashi 4 no-5 ngokulandelana.
"UColes, esitatimendeni sakhe semithombo yezindaba sangoMashi 8, wabika ukuthi njengoba kunomkhawulo wamaphakethe amane, "" izitolo eziningi zisathengisa kungakapheli ihora lokulethwa"", futhi wabiza lesi sidingo ngokuthi "" asikaze sibonakale ", " kuyilapho i-ALDI, esithombeni se-Facebook ngoLwesibili, siyibiza ngokuthi "" okungalindelekile """.
"Ngokwengimemezeli yeWoolworths, ukuthengisa kwenyuka kakhulu ngesonto eledlule".
Isitolo sikaCostco eCanberra naso sakhawulela inani elivunyelwe emaphaketheni amabili ngesonto eledlule.
Ukuze kuqhubeke kuncishiswe ukushoda, uColes wa-oda amaphakheji amakhulu kubaphakeli futhi wandisa imvamisa yokulethwa, iWoolworths ya-oda isitoko esengeziwe, kuyilapho i-ALDI yenza isitoko se-Special Wednesday ehleliwe sitholakale kusenesikhathi.
URussell Zimmerman, umqondisi ophethe we - Australian Retailers Association, wathi abathengisi bazama ukuthola amasheya, kodwa imithetho yendawo ephathelene nesikhathi sokulethwa kwezimpahla ngamaloli yenza kube nzima.
Ulindele izindleko zokukhiqiza ezikhulayo, njengoba abahlinzeki bezama ukuhlangabezana nesidingo, kanye nokuncishiswa kokukhethekile.
NgoLwesibili, i-ALDI imemezele ukuthi ngenxa yokukhishwa kwamasheya kusenesikhathi, ezinye izitolo azikwazi ukuhambisa izimpahla ezihlukile ngoLwesithathu.
Embikweni we - News.com.au, uDkt. Gary Mortimer, onguchwepheshe wezokuthengisa wase - Queensland University of Technology, wathi izitolo zigcwalisa isitoko njalo ebusuku.
Uthe iphepha langasese liyinto enkulu, okuholela ekutheni kube nenani elincane lezinqolobane, futhi uma lithengisiwe, kushiya izindawo eziningi zamashalofu zingenalutho, okwenza kube nomuzwa wokuntuleka.
I-Coles ne-Woolworths banombono wokuthi uma bekukhona izinto eziningi eshalofini, uma umkhiqizo onjengezindwangu zangasese kanye ne-sanitizer kungathengwa futhi kukhona ngobuningi, cishe ubungeke ukunciphisa ukwethuka kusho uRussell Zimmerman nge-ABC News.
Umkhiqizi wephepha langasese elenziwe kabusha i-Who Gives a Crap uthe ngoLwesithathu olwedlule ukuthi isiphelile isitoko.
I-Kimberly-Clark, ekhiqiza i-Kleenex Toilet Tissue, ne-Solaris Paper ekhiqiza i-Sorbent, bagcizelele ukuthi basebenza amahora angu-24/7 ukuze balondoloze ukunikezwa, ngokusho kombiko weNews.com.au.
I-Domain.com, ingosi yezezakhiwo, yabika abanye abathengisi bezindlu ababenikela ngephepha langasese mahhala kumuntu owenza inani lokuqala ngokuthengiswa kwezakhiwo eMelbourne, lapho inani lezakhiwo ezazithengiswa lalingekho ngenxa yokuthi abathengi babe nesikhathi sokuphumula ngempelasonto ende yoSuku Lwezisebenzi.
Uhlelo lwangoLwesine lwe-NT News, iphephandaba lansuku zonke elinyatheliswa eDarwin, lwaluhlanganisa isihloko esifakwe ngamakhasi ayisishiyagalombili esasihloselwe ukusikwa futhi sisetshenziswe njengamaphepha okugeza.
Izitolo ekuqaleni zazingafuni ukubeka imikhawulo, ngokusho kombiko ovela kwa-ABC Australia ngoMashi 3 lapho bethi babengenayo inhloso yokufaka imikhawulo ekuthengeni.
URussell Zimmerman wengeze ngokuthi eminye imikhiqizo nayo idingeka kakhulu, kuhlanganise imaski, i-sanitiser, ukudla okomile, ukugeza izandla kanye nomfula.
Ngokufanayo, ngaphandle kwe-Australia, ngeSonto kusihlwa esitolo esikhulu saseBrithani i-Ocado satholakala sinciphisa ukuthengwa kwephepha langasese lika-Andres libe amaphakethe amabili angu-12.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba imemezela ukuthi i-COVID-19 iyisifo esiwubhubhane
NgoLwesithathu, i-World Health Organization (WHO) yamemezela ukuqubuka okuqhubekayo kwe-COVID-19 - isifo esibangelwa i-coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 - njengobhubhane.
"Nakuba igama elithi ""umqedazwe"" libhekisela kuphela ekutheni isifo sisakazeke kangakanani, hhayi ukuthi izigameko ezithile ziyingozi kangakanani, i-WHO yaphawula isidingo sokushayela ohulumeni ukuba bathathe izinyathelo:"
Wonke amazwe asengaguqula inkambo yalolu bhubhane.
Uma amazwe ethola, ahlola, elapha, ehlukanisa, elandelela futhi eqoqa abantu bawo ekuphenduleni, kusho uTedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, uMqondisi-Jikelele we-WHO.
Sikhathazeke kakhulu ngezinga elikhathazayo lokusabalala nobunzima kanye nezinga elikhathazayo lokungenzi lutho.
"Ngokusho kukaDkt Tom Frieden, owayengumqondisi we-United States' Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, ubhadane lwe-COVID-19 "lungazange lube khona".
"Wathi, emazwini ashicilelwe yi-CNN ngoFebhuwari, ""ngaphandle komkhuhlane, awukho omunye igciwane lokuphefumula eliye lalandelwa kusukela ekuqhamukeni kuya ekusakazekeni okuqhubekayo emhlabeni jikelele. """
"UGhebreyesus waveza umbono ofanayo, ethi ""asikaze sibone ubhubhane olubangelwa i-coronavirus".""
"Waqhubeka wathi, ""futhi asikaze siwubone ubhubhane olungase lulawulwe ngesikhathi esifanayo"."""
Isimo esisha njengobhadane silandela isinqumo se-WHO ngoJanuwari sokumemezela ukuqubuka njengesixazululo esiphuthumayo sezempilo yomphakathi esiyinkathazo yamazwe omhlaba.
"Umqondisi we-United States' National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease, uDkt Anthony Fauci, uthe ngokuqubuka kwalolu bhubhane, ""ngokuyisisekelo, kuzoba kubi kakhulu"."
NgoLwesine, i-Associated Press ibike ukuthi okungenani kunamacala ayi-126,000 e-COVID-19 emhlabeni wonke, okuholele ekufeni kwabantu abangaphezu kuka-4 600.
Ubhubhane lwe-coronavirus lwango-2019-20 luyisifo esiqhubekayo sesifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), esibangelwa i-coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) enesifo sokuphefumula esibi.
Ukuqubuka kwabonwa eWuhan, eChina, ngoDisemba 2019, kwachazwa njengesifo sezempilo esiphuthumayo esiyinkinga yomphakathi emhlabeni jikelele ngoJanuwari 30, 2020, futhi kwabhekwa njengobhubhane mhlaka 11 Mashi 2020.
Kusukela ngo-Ephreli 10, 2020, cishe amacala ayizigidi eziyi-1.61 e-COVID-19 abikiwe emazweni nasezifundeni ezingama-210, okwaholela ekufeni kwabantu abangaba ngu-97 000.
Abantu abangaba ngu-364,000 sebelulama.
Izinga lokufa kwabantu eChina lilinganiswe ukuthi liyi-4%, kanti emhlabeni wonke lisukela ku-13.04% e-Algeria kuya ku-0.08% eNew Zealand.
Izimpawu ezivamile zihlanganisa umkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela nokuphefumula kanzima.
Izinkinga zingase zihlanganise i-pneumonia kanye ne-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Isikhathi esivela ekuchayekeni kuze kuvele izimpawu ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu, kodwa singahluka kusuka ezinsukwini ezimbili kuya kwezingu-14.
Alikho igciwane elaziwayo noma indlela yokwelapha i - virus.
Ukwelashwa okuyinhloko ukwelashwa okubonisa izimpawu nokweseka. Izinyathelo eziphakanyisiwe zokuvimbela zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukumboza umlomo lapho umuntu ekhwehlela, ukugcina ibanga kwabanye abantu, nokuqapha nokuzihlukanisa kwabantu abasolwa ukuthi banegciwane.
Izikhulu zikahulumeni emhlabeni wonke ziye zaphendula ngokubeka imingcele ekuhambeni, ukuvalela abantu bodwa, imithetho yokufika ekhaya, ukulawula izingozi zasemsebenzini, nokuvala izikhungo.
Lesi sifo siholele ekuphazamisekeni okukhulu kwezomnotho kwezenhlalo, ukumiswa noma ukukhanselwa kwemicimbi yezemidlalo, yezenkolo, yezombusazwe neyezamasiko, kanye nokuntuleka kwempahla okwandile okwenziwa kubi kakhulu ukuthenga ngokweqile.
Izikole namayunivesithi kuvaliwe noma ezweni lonke noma ezindaweni ezithile emazweni angu-193, kuthinta cishe amaphesenti angu-99.4 abafundi emhlabeni.
Imininingwane eyiphutha ngaleli gciwane isakazeke ku-inthanethi, futhi kube nezigameko zokwenyanya abantu bakwamanye amazwe kanye nokucwaswa kwabantu baseChina, abanye abantu abavela eMpumalanga naseNingizimu-mpumalanga ye-Asia kanye nokubukeka kwabo, nabanye abavela ezindaweni ezinezimo eziphawulekayo zaleli gciwane.
Ngenxa yokuncishiswa kokuhamba nokuvalwa kwezimboni ezisindayo, kube nokwehla kokungcoliswa komoya nokukhishwa kwekhabhoni.
Iziphathimandla zezempilo eWuhan, eChina (inhloko-dolobha yesifundazwe saseHubei) zabika isiqephu samacala ephemoniya anesizathu esingaziwa ngoDisemba 31, 2019, futhi kwaqalwa uphenyo ekuqaleni kukaJanuwari 2020.
Izimo eziningi zazinokuxhumana neMakethe Yokuthengisa Izinkomo ZaseHuanan ngakho-ke kucatshangwa ukuthi igciwane linomsuka wezilwane.
Igciwane elibangele ukuqubuka laziwa ngokuthi i-SARS-CoV-2, igciwane elisanda kutholakala elihlobene kakhulu nama-bat coronaviruses, ama-pangolin coronaviruses, ne-SARS-CoV. Umuntu wokuqala owaziwayo onempawu kamuva watholakala ukuthi ugule ngomhlaka-1 kuDisemba 2019, futhi lowo muntu wayengenazo izixhumanisi ezibonakalayo neqoqo lemakethe elimanzi kamuva.
Eqenjini lokuqala lamacala abikwe ngoDisemba 2019, izingxenye ezimbili kwezintathu zatholakala ukuthi zihlobene nemakethe.
Ngo-13 Mashi 2020, umbiko ongaqinisekisiwe we-South China Morning Post wasikisela ukuthi icala elaqala ngo-17 Novemba 2019, kumuntu oneminyaka engu-55 ubudala ovela esifundazweni saseHubei, kungenzeka ukuthi laliyisifo sokuqala. Ngo-26 Febhuwari 2020, i-WHO yabika ukuthi, njengoba amacala amasha kubikwa ukuthi anciphile eChina kodwa anda ngokuzumayo e-Italy, e-Iran naseNingizimu Korea, inani lamacala amasha ngaphandle kweChina lidlule inani lamacala amasha ngaphakathi kweChina okokuqala ngqa.
Kungase kube khona ukungabikho okuphawulekayo kwamacala, ikakhulukazi kulabo abanezimpawu ezincane.
NgoFebhuwari 26, amacala ambalwa kakhulu ayebikiwe kubantu abasha, kanti labo abaneminyaka engu-19 nangaphansi benza ama-2.4 ekhulwini lamacala emhlabeni wonke. Umeluleki oyinhloko wezesayensi wase-United Kingdom, uPatrick Vallance, walinganisela ukuthi u-60% wabantu baseBrithani kuzodingeka ukuthi baguleleke ngaphambi kokuba kutholakale amasosha omzimba asebenzayo.
Amacala abhekisela enanini labantu abaye bahlolwa i-COVID-19, futhi okuqinisekiswe ukuthi bane-COVID-19 ngokwama-protocol asemthethweni.
Kusukela ngomhlaka 23 Mashi, alikho izwe elabe selihlole abantu abangaphezu kuka-3% wabantu balo, futhi amazwe amaningi abe nezinqubomgomo ezisemthethweni zokungahloli labo abanezimpawu eziwuphawu nje, njenge-Italy, iNetherlands, iSpain, neSwitzerland.
Ucwaningo olushicilelwe ngo-16 Mashi luthole ukuthi eChina, kuze kube u-23 Januwari, kulinganiselwa ukuthi ama-86% okutheleleka nge-COVID-19 ayengatholakali, nokuthi lokhu kuthinteka okungakaze kubhalwe phansi kwakuwumthombo wokutheleleka wama-79% amacala abhalwe phansi.
Ukuhlaziywa kwezibalo okukhishwe ngo-30 Mashi kulinganisela ukuthi inani lokutheleleka e-Italy lalilikhulu kakhulu kunamacala abikiwe.
Ukulinganiselwa kokuqala kwenombolo eyisisekelo yokuzala (R0) ye-COVID-19 kwakungu-1.4 kuya ku-2.4.
Ucwaningo olwanyatheliswa i-US Center for Disease Control and Prevention lwaphetha ngokuthi kungenzeka ukuthi lingu-5.7.
Abantu abaningi abane-COVID-19 bayalulama.
Kulabo abangakwenzi lokho, isikhathi esiphakathi kokuthuthukiswa kwezimpawu nokufa siye saba phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-6 nezingu-41, okuvame kakhulu ukuba izinsuku ezingu-14.
Kusukela ngo-10 Ephreli 2020, cishe abantu abangu-97,000 babebulawa yi-COVID-19.
EChina, kusukela ngo-5 February cishe u-80% wabantu abafile babephakathi kwalabo abangaphezu kuka-60, kanti u-75% babehlushwa yizinkinga zempilo ezihlanganisa izifo zenhliziyo nesifo sikashukela. Izibalo ezisemthethweni zabantu abafa ngenxa yobhubhane lwe-COVID-19 ngokuvamile zibhekisela kubantu abafa behlolwe ukuthi bane-COVID ngokuvumelana nemigomo esemthethweni.
Isibalo sangempela sabantu ababulawa yi-COVID-19 kungenzeka sibe ngaphezulu kakhulu, njengoba singase singahlanganisi abantu abafa ngaphandle kokuhlolwa - isibonelo, ekhaya, emakhaya asebekhulile, njll.
Idatha engatheni evela e-Italy ithole ukuthi inani labafile ngokweqile phakathi nalolu bhubhane lidlule inani elisemthethweni labafile be-COVID ngokuphindwe izikhathi ezi-4-5.
"Isikhulumi se-US Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) savuma ukuthi ""Siyazi ukuthi [inani labashonile elishiwo] liyisibalo esingaphansi", isitatimende esiqinisekiswe imibiko ye-anecdotal yokungabalwa kwabantu e-US. Ukubalwa kwabantu okungaphansi kuvame ukwenzeka ezimweni eziwubhubhane, njengesifo somkhuhlane wezingulube i-H1N1 ka-2009. Ukufa kokuqala okuqinisekisiwe kwaba eWuhan ngo-9 Januwari 2020. "
Ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kwezwekazi laseChina kwenzeka ngo-1 February ePhilippines, kanti ukufa kokuqala ngaphandle kwe-Asia kwaba eFrance ngo-14 February.
Ngo-February 28, ngaphandle kwezwekazi laseChina, kwabhalwa abantu abangaphezu kweshumi nesishiyagalolunye e-Iran, eNingizimu Korea nase-Italy.
NgoMashi 13, amazwe angaphezu kwamashumi amane nezindawo babike ukufa, kuwo wonke amazwekazi ngaphandle kwe-Antarctica. Izinyathelo eziningana zivame ukusetshenziselwa ukulinganisa ukufa.
Lezi zinombolo ziyahlukahluka kuye ngesifunda futhi ngokuhamba kwesikhathi, futhi zithonywa umthamo wokuhlola, ikhwalithi yohlelo lokunakekelwa kwezempilo, izinketho zokwelashwa, isikhathi esibe khona kusukela kuqubuka kuqala, kanye nezici zabantu ezifana nobudala, ubulili, kanye nempilo jikelele. Isilinganiso sokufa kuya kwecala sibonisa inani lokufa elihlukaniswe nenani lamacala atholakele esikhathini esithile.
Ngokwezibalo ze-Johns Hopkins University, isilinganiso sokufa kwabantu emhlabeni wonke sifinyelela ku-6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kusukela ngo-10 Ephreli 2020.
Inani lihlukahluka esifundeni ngasinye.
E-China, izilinganiso zesilinganiso sokufa-ku-isimo zehle zisuka ku-17.3% (kulabo abanezimpawu eziqale ngo-110 Januwari 2020) kuya ku-0.7% (kulabo abanezimpawu eziqale ngemuva kuka-1 kuFebhuwari 2020). Ezinye izilinganiso zifaka phakathi isilinganiso sokufa kwecala (CFR), esibonisa iphesenti labantu abaxilongelwe ababulawa yisifo, kanye nesilinganiso sokufa kokutheleleka (IFR), esibonisa iphesenti labantu abangenwe (abaxilongelwe nabangatholakalanga) ababulawa yisifo.
Lezi zibalo azinamkhawulo wesikhathi futhi zilandela inani elithile labantu kusukela ekungenweni kwegciwane kuze kube sekupheleni kwecala.
Izazi eziningi ziye zazama ukubala lezi zibalo zabantu abathile.
I-Center for Evidence-Based Medicine yase-University of Oxford ilinganisela ukuthi izinga lokufa ngenxa yokutheleleka kulo bhubhane lilonke liphakathi kuka-0.1% no-0.39%.
Isilinganiso esiphezulu salolu hlu sivumelana nemiphumela yokuhlolwa kokuqala nge-COVID-19 eJalimane, kanye nocwaningo lwezibalo oluhlaziya umthelela wokuhlolwa kokulinganiselwa kwe-CFR.
I-WHO ithi ubhubhane lungase lulawuleke.
Isikhathi esiphezulu nesiphelele sokuqubuka kwalesi sifo asiqinisekile futhi singahluka kuye ngendawo.
"UMaciej Boni wasePenn State University wathi, "" Uma kungalawulwa, ukuqubuka kwezifo ezithathelwanayo kuvame ukuma bese kuqala ukwehla lapho lesi sifo siphela izilwane ezingasakwazi ukuzitholela".
"Kodwa cishe akunakwenzeka ukwenza noma isiphi isiphakamiso esinengqondo manje mayelana nokuthi lokho kuyoba nini""."
Umeluleki omkhulu wezokwelapha kahulumeni waseChina uZhong Nanshan wagomela ukuthi "kungase kuphele ngoJuni" uma wonke amazwe engaqoqeka ukuba alandele izeluleko ze-WHO ngezinyathelo zokunqanda ukusabalala kwaleli gciwane.
"Ngomhlaka 17 Mashi, u-Adam Kucharski waseLondon School of Hygiene &amp; Tropical Medicine wathi i-SARS-CoV-2 ""izohlala isakazeka, mhlawumbe unyaka noma emibili"".
"Ngokusho kocwaningo lwe-Imperial College oluholwa nguNeil Ferguson, kuzodingeka ukuhlukaniswa ngokomzimba nezinye izindlela ""kuze kube yilapho sekutholakala umuthi wokugoma (okungenzeka kube izinyanga eziyi-18 noma ngaphezulu) """.
UWilliam Schaffner waseVanderbilt University uthe, "Ngicabanga ukuthi akunakwenzeka ukuthi le coronavirus - ngoba isakazeka kalula - izonyamalala ngokuphelele" futhi "ingaphenduka isifo sesizini, ibuye njalo ngonyaka".
Ukuhlasela kwalesi sifo kuncike ekutheni umhlambi unaso yini isivikelo sezilwane nokuthi kuguquka kangakanani.
Izimpawu ze-COVID-19 zingaba ezingezona eziqondile futhi abantu abanegciwane bangase bangabi nazo izimpawu.
Izimpawu ezimbili ezivame kakhulu imfiva (88%) nokukhwehlela okomile (68%).
Izimpawu ezingavamile zihlanganisa ukukhathala, ukukhiqizwa kwe-sputum yokuphefumula (i-phlegm), ukulahleka komqondo wokuhogela, ukuphefumula, ubuhlungu bemisipha namalunga, umphimbo obuhlungu, ikhanda elibuhlungu, ukuqhaqhazela, ukuhlanza, i-hemoptysis, isifo sohudo, noma i-cyanosis. I-WHO ithi cishe umuntu oyedwa kwabayisithupha uyagula kakhulu futhi abe nobunzima bokuphefumula.
I-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) ibala izimpawu eziphuthumayo ezinjengobunzima bokuphefumula, ubuhlungu besifuba obuphikelelayo noma ingcindezi, ukudideka okungazelelwe, ubunzima bokuvuka, nobuso noma izindebe ezibomvu; ukunakekelwa ngokushesha kwezokwelapha kuyelulekwa uma lezi zimpawu zikhona. Ukuthuthuka okunye kwesifo kungaholela ekutheni kube nesifo samaphaphu esibi, i-acute respiratory distress syndrome, i-sepsis, i-septic shock nokufa.
Abanye balabo abangenwe yilesi sifo bangase bangabi nazo izimpawu, kodwa imiphumela yokuhlolwa iqinisekisa ukuthi banaso, ngakho abacwaningi banikeze iseluleko sokuthi labo abaxhumana eduze nabantu abangenwe yilesi sifo kufanele babhekwe futhi bahlolwe ukuze kulahlwe ukuthi banaso yini.
Izibalo zaseChina zesilinganiso sabantu abangenazo izimpawu zihamba kusuka kwabambalwa kuya kuma-44%.
Isikhathi esivamile sokufukamela (isikhathi esiphakathi kokutheleleka nokuqala kwezimpawu) sisukela ezinsukwini ezi-1 kuya kwezi-14; ngokuvamile siyizinsuku ezinhlanu. Njengesibonelo sokungaqiniseki, isilinganiso senani labantu abane-COVID-19 abalahlekelwa umuzwa wabo wokuhogela ekuqaleni kwakungu-30% futhi kamuva sehle saba ngu-15%.
Eminye imininingwane yokuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kanjani isazolungiswa.
Kukholelwa ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka ikakhulukazi ngesikhathi sokuxhumana eduze nangamaconsi amancane akhiqizwa ngesikhathi sokukhwehlela, ukuthimula noma ukukhuluma; lapho ukuhlangana eduze kungamamitha angu-1 kuya kwangu-2 (amamitha amathathu kuya kwangu-6).
Ucwaningo luye lwathola ukuthi ukukhwehlela okungagqwaliwe kungaholela ekutheni amaconsi ahambe afinyelele kumamitha angu-4.5 kuya kumamitha angu-8.2.
Abanye baye basikisela ukuthi leli gciwane lingadluliselwa ngamaconsi amancane ahlala isikhathi eside emoyeni, angahle abe khona ngesikhathi sokukhuluma. Amaconsi okuphefumula nawo angahle abe khona ngesikhathi sokuphefumula, kuhlanganise nalapho ukhuluma, nakuba leli gciwane ngokuvamile lingahlalwa umoya.
La mathonsi angangena emlonyeni noma ekhaleni labantu abaseduze noma mhlawumbe angene emaphashini.
Ezinye izinqubo zezokwelapha ezinjengokufakwa umjovo kanye nokusiza umuntu ukuba aphile (CPR) zingase zenze ukuba uketshezi oluphuma emithambo yokuphefumula lube yi-aerosol futhi ngaleyo ndlela kuholele ekusakazekeni emoyeni.
Ingase futhi isakazeke lapho umuntu ethinta indawo engcolisiwe, kuhlanganise nesikhumba, bese ethinta amehlo, ikhala noma umlomo.
Nakuba kunokukhathazeka ngokuthi ingase isakazeke ngokuthululwa, le ngozi kuthiwa incane.
Uhulumeni waseChina waphika ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi i-SARS-CoV-2 ingadluliselwa ngomlomo noma ngezitho zangasese. Leli gciwane lithelelana kakhulu ezinsukwini ezintathu zokuqala ngemva kokuqala kwezimpawu, nakuba kungenzeka ukuthi lisakazeke ngaphambi kokuba kuvele izimpawu futhi nasezigabeni zakamuva zesifo.
Abantu baye bathola imiphumela emihle yalesi sifo ezinsukwini ezintathu ngaphambi kokuqala kwezimpawu okusikisela ukuthi ukudluliselwa kungenzeka ngaphambi kokuthuthukisa izimpawu ezinkulu.
Imibiko embalwa kuphela yamacala angenazo izimpawu aqinisekiswe elebhu, kodwa ukutheleleka okungenazo izimpawu sekubonwe ngamanye amazwe ngesikhathi kwenziwa uphenyo lokufuna abantu abathintekile.
I-European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control (ECDC) ithi nakuba kungacaci kahle ukuthi lesi sifo sisakazeka kalula kangakanani, umuntu oyedwa ngokuvamile uthelela abanye ababili kuya kwabathathu. Igciwane lisinda amahora noma izinsuku ezindaweni.
Ngokuqondile, leli gciwane litholakala kuze kube yizinsuku ezintathu epulasitiki (i-polypropylene) kanye nensimbi engagqwali engu-304, usuku olulodwa kukhadibhodi, futhi kuze kube ngamahora amane kukaphayi.
Nokho, lokhu kuyahlukahluka kuye ngokuthi umswakama kanye nokushisa. Izilwane ezifuyiwe nezinye izilwane ziye zahlolwa ukuthi azinayo i-COVID-19.
Abukho ubufakazi bokuthi izilwane zingalidlulisela kubantu leli gciwane, nakuba iziphathimandla zaseBrithani zeluleka umuntu ukuba ageze izandla zakhe ngemva kokuthintana nezilwane, njengokungathi ngemva kokuthintana nezinye izinto abantu abangase bazithinte.
I-coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) iyinhlobo entsha yegciwane, eyahlukaniswa okokuqala kubantu abathathu abane-pneumonia abaxhumene neqoqo lamagciwane ezifo zokuphefumula e-Wuhan.
Zonke izici zegciwane elisha i-SARS-CoV-2 zenzeka kuma-coronaviruses ahlobene emvelweni. Ngaphandle komzimba womuntu, leli gciwane libulawa insipho yasendlini, echitha isembozo sayo esivikelayo. I-SARS-CoV-2 ihlobene kakhulu ne-SARS-CoV yokuqala.
Kucatshangwa ukuthi kunomsuka wezifo ezibangelwa izilwane.
Ukuhlaziywa kwezakhi zofuzo kuveze ukuthi i-coronavirus ihlangana ngezakhi zofuzo nohlobo lwe-Betacoronavirus, ku-subgenus Sarbecovirus (uhlu lwe-B) kanye nezinhlobo ezimbili ezithathwe kumalulwane.
Ifana ngo-96% ezingeni le-genome ephelele namanye amasampula e-coronavirus yamalulwane (i-BatCov RaTG13).
NgoFebhuwari 2020, abacwaningi baseChina bathola ukuthi kunomehluko owodwa kuphela we-amino acid ezingxenyeni ezithile zokulandelana kwe-genome phakathi kwamagciwane avela kuma-pangolin nalawo avela kubantu.
Ukuqhathaniswa kwe-genome ephelele kuze kube manje kutholakale okungenani ama-92% ezakhi zofuzo ezabiwe phakathi kwe-pangolin coronavirus ne-SARS-CoV-2, okunganele ukufakazela ukuthi ama-pangolin yiwona aphethe.
Ukutheleleka ngegciwane kungaxilongwa okwesikhashana ngesisekelo sezimpawu, nakuba ukuqinisekiswa ekugcineni kungokuphenduka kokudluliselwa kwe-polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) kwezikhala ezihlaselwe noma i-CT imaging.
Ucwaningo olwaluthelekisa i-PCR ne-CT eWuhan lwabonisa ukuthi i-CT ibukhali kakhulu kune-PCR, nakuba ingacacile kangako, futhi izici zayo eziningi zokuthwebula izithombe zifana nezinye izifo zemiphunga kanye nezinqubo zezifo.
"Ngo-March 2020, i-American College of Radiology incoma ukuthi ""i-CT akufanele isetshenziselwe ukuhlola noma njengesivivinyo sokuqala sokuxilonga i-COVID-19"."
I-WHO ishicilele izinqubo zokuhlola i-RNA eziningana ze-SARS-CoV-2, eyokuqala yakhishwa ngo-17 Januwari.
Ukuhlola kusebenzisa i-reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) yesikhathi sangempela.
Ukuhlola kungenziwa kumasampula okuphefumula noma egazi.
Imiphumela ivame ukutholakala kungakapheli amahora ambalwa noma izinsuku.
Ngokuvamile lokhu kuhlolwa kwenziwa kusampula ye-nasopharyngeal nakuba kungasetshenziswa nesampula yomphimbo. Amalabhorethri amaningi nezinkampani zenza ukuhlolwa kwe-serological, okuveza ama-antibody.
Kusukela ngo-6 Ephreli 2020, akukho kulokhu okuboniswe ukuthi kunembe ngokwanele ukuthi kuvunyelwe ukusetshenziswa kabanzi.
E-US, ukuhlolwa kwe-serological okuthuthukiswe yi-Cellex kugunyaziwe ukusetshenziswa kwezimo eziphuthumayo kuphela ngama-laboratories aqinisekisiwe.
Izici ezivelele zokuqoshwa kwe-radiographs kanye ne-computed tomography (CT) yabantu abanezimpawu zihlanganisa ukungafani kwe-opacities ye-glass ephansi ephansi kanye nokungabikho kwe-pleural effusions.
I-Italian Radiological Society ihlanganisa i-database yamazwe omhlaba eku-inthanethi yemiphumela yokuthwebula izithombe ezimweni eziqinisekisiwe.
Ngenxa yokweqisana nezinye izifo ezifana ne-adenovirus, ukuhlola izithombe ngaphandle kokuqinisekiswa yi-PCR kunokucaciswa okulinganiselwe ekuboneni i-COVID-19.
Ucwaningo olukhulu olwenziwa eChina lwaqhathanisa imiphumela ye-CT yesifuba ne-PCR futhi lwabonisa ukuthi nakuba ukubonwa ngeso lengqondo kungabonakali kakhulu ngokutheleleka, kuyashesha futhi kuyashesha, okusikisela ukuthi kufanele kubhekwe njengethuluzi lokuhlola ezindaweni ezinesifo esiwumqedazwe.
Izinhlelo ze-convolutional neural networks ezisekelwe ekwazini okufakelwayo zenzelwe ukuthola izici zokuhlolwa kwegciwane nge-X-ray kanye ne-CT.
Amasu okuvimbela ukudluliselwa kwalesi sifo ahlanganisa ukugcina inhlanzeko yomuntu siqu, ukugeza izandla, ukugwema ukuthinta amehlo, ikhala noma umlomo ngezandla ezingahlanjiwe, nokukhwehlela noma ukuthimula uthinte isikhwama bese ufaka isikhwama ngqo emgodleni wokulahla udoti.
Labo okungenzeka ukuthi sebevele banalo igciwane baye belulekwa ukuba bagqoke imaski yokuhlinza lapho bephakathi kwabantu.
Kunconywa futhi izindlela zokuzihlukanisa ukuze kuvikelwe ukutheleleka. Ohulumeni abaningi baye bavimbela noma batusa ukuba abantu bangahambi uma kungadingekile ukuba baye noma babuye emazweni noma ezindaweni ezithintwe yilesi sifo.
Nokho, leli gciwane selifinyelele esigabeni sokusakazeka komphakathi ezingxenyeni ezinkulu zomhlaba.
Lokhu kusho ukuthi igciwane lisakazeka ngaphakathi kwemiphakathi, futhi amanye amalungu omphakathi awazi ukuthi athelelekephi noma kanjani. Abahlinzeki bezempilo abanakekela umuntu okungenzeka ukuthi uthelelekile bayelulekwa ukuthi basebenzise izindlela ezijwayelekile zokuqapha, izindlela zokuqapha lapho umuntu ethinta umuntu, kanye nokuvikela amehlo. Ukulandelela umuntu othintekile kuyindlela ebalulekile yeziphathimandla zezempilo yokunquma umthombo wokutheleleka nokuvimbela ukudluliswa okunye.
Ukusetshenziswa kolwazi lwendawo kusuka kumakhalekhukhwini nguhulumeni ngale njongo kuye kwabangela ukukhathazeka ngemfihlo, ne-Amnesty International kanye nezinye izinhlangano ezingaphezu kwe-100 ezikhishwa isitatimende esicela imikhawulo kulolu hlobo lokuqapha.
