"Ukulawulwa kokuhamba komphakathi kwasetshenziswa emadolobheni amaningi, futhi kulinganiselwa ukuthi abantu abangaba yizigidi ezingu-760 (abangaphezu kwengxenye yabantu) babhekene nohlobo oluthile lokunqandwa ngaphandle. Ngemva kokuba ukuqubuka kwalesi sifo kungene esigabeni salo somhlaba wonke ngoMashi, iziphathimandla zaseChina zathatha izinyathelo eziqinile zokuvimbela igciwane ukuba ""lingene"" kwamanye amazwe".
Isibonelo, iBeijing inqume ukuvalelwa izinsuku ezingu-14 okuyimpoqo kubo bonke abahambi bamazwe angaphandle abangena edolobheni. NgoMashi 23, iChina eyayisezweni lonke yayitholwe igciwane elilodwa kuphela ezinsukwini ezinhlanu ezedlule, kulokhu ngomhambi obuya eGuangzhou evela e-Istanbul.
