Ngawo lowo mhla imingcele yokuhamba yehliswa eHubei, ngaphandle kwaseWuhan, izinyanga ezimbili ngemuva kokuthi kufakwe ukuvalwa. UMnyango Wezangaphandle waseChina wamemezela ngo-26 Mashi 2020 ukuthi ukungena kwabanama-visa noma abanemvume yokuhlala kuzomiswa kusukela ngo-28 Mashi, ngaphandle kwemininingwane ethile yokuthi le nqubomgomo izophela nini.
Labo abafisa ukungena eChina kuzodingeka bafake isicelo se-visa emakhonsulenini noma emishinini yaseChina.
