I-COVID-19 yaqinisekiswa ukuthi isakazeke eNingizimu Korea ngo-20 Januwari 2020 isuka eChina.
I-ejensi yezempilo yaleli lizwe ibike ukwanda okuphawulekayo kwamacala aqinisekisiwe ngo-Febhuwari 20, ikakhulukazi ngenxa yokuhlangana eDaegu kwenhlangano entsha yenkolo eyaziwa ngokuthi iShincheonji Church of Jesus.
Kwakusolwa ukuthi ukuqubuka kwalesi sifo kwabangelwa abalandeli bakaShincheonji ababevakashele iDaegu bevela eWuhan.
Kusukela ngoFebhuwari 22, phakathi kwabalandeli besonto abangu-9,336, abangu- 1,261 noma cishe u-13% babika izimpawu. INingizimu Korea yamemezela izinga eliphezulu kakhulu lokuxwayisa ngoFebhuwari 23, 2020.
NgoFebhuwari 28, kwabikwa iziguli ezingaphezu kuka-2 000 eKorea, ezakhuphuka zaba ngu-3 150 ngoFebhuwari 29.
Zonke izikhungo zempi zaseNingizimu Korea zafakwa endaweni yokuvalelwa ngemuva kokuhlolwa kwaqinisekisa ukuthi amasosha amathathu ayithole i-virus.
Izinhlelo zezindiza nazo zathinteka ngakho-ke zashintshwa. INingizimu Korea yaqala lokho okwakubhekwa njengohlelo olukhulu kakhulu noluhlelelwe kahle kakhulu emhlabeni wonke lokuhlola abantu ukuthi abanale gciwane, nokuhlukanisa noma yibaphi abantu abanalo kanye nokulandela nokuvalela labo abaxhumana nabo.
Izindlela zokuhlolwa zazihlanganisa ukuzibika okuyimpoqo kwezimpawu ngabasanda kufika emazweni omhlaba ngokusebenzisa uhlelo lokusebenza lweselula, ukuhlolwa kwegciwane ngokuhamba ngemoto imiphumela itholakale ngosuku olulandelayo, kanye nokwandisa ikhono lokuhlolwa ukuze kuvunyelwe abantu abangafika ku-20 000 ukuba bahlolwe nsuku zonke.
Uhlelo lwaseNingizimu Korea lubhekwa njengoluphumelele ekulawuleni ukuqubuka yize kungafakwanga amadolobha wonke endaweni yokuvalelwa. Umphakathi waseNingizimu Korea ekuqaleni wahlukaniswa ukusabela kukaMengameli uMun Jae-in kulolu sizi.
Abantu abaningi baseKorea basayina izicelo zokucela ukuba uMong Moon asuswe esikhundleni ngenxa yalokho abakushoyo ukuthi uhulumeni awuphathanga kahle lo bhubhane, noma ukudumisa indlela asabela ngayo.
NgoMashi 23, kwabikwa ukuthi iNingizimu Korea yayinomthamo ophansi kakhulu wosuku olulodwa emavikini amane.
NgoMashi 29 kwabikwa ukuthi kusukela ngo-April 1 bonke abafika phesheya kwezilwandle bazogcinwa bevalelwe amasonto amabili.
Ngokwemibiko yabezindaba ngomhlaka-1 ku-Ephreli, iNingizimu Korea ithole izicelo zosizo lokuhlola igciwane ezivela emazweni ahlukene ayi-121.
I-Iran yabika amacala ayo okuqala aqinisekisiwe okutheleleka nge-SARS-CoV-2 ngo-19 February eQom, lapho, ngokusho koMnyango Wezempilo Nezemfundo Yezokwelapha, abantu ababili bashona kamuva ngalolo suku.
Izinyathelo zokuqala ezamenyezelwa uhulumeni zazihlanganisa ukwesulwa kwamakhonsathi neminye imicimbi yamasiko, imicimbi yezemidlalo, nemikhuleko yangoLwesihlanu, nokuvalwa kwamanyuvesi, izikhungo zemfundo ephakeme, nezikole.
I-Iran yabela ama-rials ayizigidi eziyizinkulungwane ezinhlanu ukuze ilwe naleli gciwane.
UMengameli Hassan Rouhani uthe ngoFebhuwari 26 2020 ukuthi kwakungekho izinhlelo zokuvalela abantu ezindaweni ezithintwe ukuqubuka, futhi kwakuzoba ngabantu kuphela abazofakwa endaweni yokuvalelwa.
Izinhlelo zokunciphisa ukuhamba phakathi kwamadolobha zamenyezelwa ngoMashi, yize izimoto eziningi phakathi kwamadolobha zaqhubeka ngaphambi koNyaka Omusha wasePheresiya uNawruz.
Izindawo ezingcwele zamaShiya eQom zahlala zivulekile kubahambi ngezinyawo kuze kube mhla zi-16 kuMashi 2020. I-Iran yaba yisikhungo sokusabalala kwegciwane ngemuva kweChina ngoFebhuwari.
Phakathi nezinsolo zokufihla ubukhulu bokugqashuka kwalesi sifo e-Iran, amazwe angaphezu kwayishumi ayeseke amacala awo emuva e-Iran ngoFebhuwari 28, okukhombisa ukuthi ubukhulu bokugqashuka kungenzeka bube nzima kakhulu kunamacala angama-388 abikwe nguhulumeni wase-Iran ngalolo suku.
IPhalamende lase-Iran lavalwa, kwathi amalungu alo angu-23 kwangu-290 abikwa ukuthi ahlolwe atholakala enegciwane ngo-3 Mashi.
Ngo-March 12, i-Human Rights Watch yanxusa iziphathimandla zasejele zase-Iran ukuba zidedele ngaphandle kwemibandela izishoshovu zamalungelo abantu ezivalelwe ngenxa yokungavumelani ngokuthula, futhi futhi zidedele okwesikhashana zonke iziboshwa ezifanelekile.
Lithi kunengozi enkulu yokusabalala kwegciwane ezikhungweni ezivaliwe ezifana nezindawo zokuvalelwa, nazo ezingenazo izinsiza zokwelashwa ezanele.
Ngo-March 15, uhulumeni wase-Iran wabika ukuthi abantu abangu-100 babulawa ngosuku olulodwa, okuyinani eliphakeme kakhulu elabhalwa kuleli lizwe selokhu kwaqala ukuqubuka.
Okungenani osopolitiki abangu-12 abasebenza noma ababekade besebenza e-Iran kanye nezikhulu zikahulumeni base bebulewe yilesi sifo ngo-Mashi 17.
Ngo-23 Mashi, i-Iran yayithola iziguli ezintsha ezingu-50 njalo ngehora kanye nokufa okusha njalo ngemizuzu eyishumi ngenxa ye-coronavirus.
Ngokwesikhulu se-WHO, kungenzeka ukuthi kuneziguli eziphindwe kahlanu e-Iran kunalokho okubikwayo.
Kusikisela nokuthi izingqinamba zase-U.S. ku-Iran kungenzeka zithinta ikhono lezwe lezezimali lokusabela ekuqubukeni kwegciwane.
I-UN High Commissioner for Human Rights icele ukuthi kuncishiswe izigwebo zezomnotho ezibekelwe amazwe athinteke kakhulu yilolu bhubhane, kuhlanganise ne-Iran.
