"Kusevele kwenziwe isinqumo sokuthi kumiswe imisebenzi nemicimbi yezemidlalo kulezo zindawo. ""Ngomhlaka-4 Mashi, uhulumeni wase-Italy wayala ukuvalwa ngokuphelele kwazo zonke izikole namanyuvesi ezweni lonke njengoba i-Italy yafinyelela kubantu abafile abangu-100".
