Iqembu labachwepheshe lithi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokuthola usizo lokukhulula impilo futhi uhulumeni unalo lomthwalo.
Leli qembu lagcizelela ukuthi ukuntuleka kwemithombo noma umshuwalense wezempilo akufanele neze kube yisisusa sokubandlulula iqembu elithile.
Ochwepheshe bagcizelele ukuthi wonke umuntu unelungelo lokuthola impilo, kuhlanganise nabantu abakhubazekile, amalungu amaqembu amancane, abantu abadala, abantu abaxoshiwe emakhaya abo, abantu abangenamakhaya, labo abaphila ezimweni ezimbi kakhulu, abantu ababoshiwe, kanye nababaleki kanye namanye amaqembu angachazwanga adinga ukwesekwa uhulumeni.
Izinhlangano zikahulumeni zamazwe omhlaba zibhekene nemiphumela yezomnotho neyenhlalo yenkinga ye-COVID-19.
I-Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (i-OECD) isungule isiteji sokunikeza ulwazi olufika ngesikhathi noluphelele ngezimpendulo zenqubomgomo emazweni emhlabeni wonke, kanye nemibono kanye nezeluleko.
