Ukuqubuka kwe-coronavirus kusolwe ngezikhathi eziningana zokushoda kokunikezwa, okuvela ekusetshenzisweni okwandisiwe kwemishini ukulwa nokuqubuka, ukuthenga ukwethuka, kanye nokuphazamiseka kokusebenza kwefektri nokusebenza kwempahla.
I-United States Food and Drug Administration ikhiphe izixwayiso mayelana nokushoda kwemithi nemishini yezokwelapha ngenxa yokwanda kwesidingo sabathengi nokuphazamiseka kwabahlinzeki.
Izindawo eziningana nazo zabona ukuthenga kwabantu ngokuthuthumela okuholele ekutheni kuhlanzwe emashalofini izimpahla zokudla ezifana nokudla, iphepha langasese, namanzi asemabhodleleni, okwaholela ekushodeni kokutholakala.
Imboni yezobuchwepheshe ikakhulukazi ibilokhu ixwayisa ngokulibaziseka kokuthunyelwa kwezimpahla zobuchwepheshe.
Ngokwomqondisi - jikelele we - WHO uTedros Adhanom, isidingo semishini yokuzivikela siqu sesiphindeke izikhathi eziyikhulu.
Lokhu kubiza kuye kwaholela ekukhuphukeni kwamanani aphindwe izikhathi ezingamashumi amabili kunamanani avamile futhi kwabangela ukubambezeleka kokunikezwa kwempahla yezokwelapha izinyanga ezine kuya kweziyisithupha.
Futhi kubangele ukuntuleka kwemishini yokuzivikela emhlabeni wonke, i-WHO ixwayisa ngokuthi lokhu kuzobeka abasebenzi bezempilo engozini.
E-Australia, ubhadane lunikeze abathengi be-daigou ithuba elisha lokuthengisa imikhiqizo yase-Australia eChina.
