Ukugeza izandla, okwaziwa nangokuthi ukuhlanzeka kwezandla, kuwukuhlanza izandla ngenjongo yokususa inhlabathi, amafutha, amagciwane, noma ezinye izinto ezingadingeki.
"Ukugeza izandla ngensipho njalo ngezikhathi ezithile" ezibalulekile "ngosuku kuvimbela ukusabalala kwezifo eziningi, isibonelo isifo sohudo nekholera, ezidluliselwa ngendlela yokuhlanza noma ukugeza".
Abantu bangatholwa nezifo zokuphefumula ezinjengomkhuhlane noma umkhuhlane ovamile, ngokwesibonelo, uma bengazihlanzi izandla zabo ngaphambi kokuthinta amehlo, ikhala, noma umlomo (okungukuthi, ulwelwesi olune-mucous).
Izikhathi ezinhlanu ezibucayi phakathi nosuku lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile zihlanganisa: ngaphambi nangemva kokwenza indle, ngemva kokuhlanza izinsini zengane noma ukushintsha amaphayiphu, ngaphambi kokondla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi nangemva kokulungisa ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi, noma izinkukhu.
Uma amanzi nensipho kungatholakali, izandla zingahlanzwa ngomlotha. I-World Health Organization incoma ukugeza izandla:
Ngaphambi, phakathi, nangemva kokulungiselela ukudla.
Ngaphambi nangemva kokunakekela umuntu ogulayo.
Ngemva kokushintsha u-diaper noma ukuhlanza ingane eseyihambe.
Ngemva kokukhwehlela noma ukuthimula.
Ngemva kokuthinta isilwane, ukudla kwezilwane noma udoti wezilwane.
Ukuhlanzeka kwezandla kwezokwelapha kubhekisele emikhubeni yokuhlanzeka ehlobene nezinqubo zezokwelapha.
Ukugeza izandla ngaphambi kokunikeza umuthi noma ukunakekela kwezokwelapha kungavimbela noma kunciphise ukusabalala kwezifo.
Injongo eyinhloko yokwelashwa yokugeza izandla ukuhlanza izandla kumagciwane (ama-bacterium, amagciwane, noma ezinye izinto ezincane eziphilayo ezingabangela izifo) kanye namakhemikhali angadala ukulimala noma izifo.
Lokhu kubaluleke kakhulu kubantu abasebenza ngokudla noma abasebenza emkhakheni wezokwelapha, kodwa futhi kuwumkhuba obalulekile emphakathini jikelele.
Ukugeza izandla kunemivuzo eminingi empilweni, okuhlanganisa ukunciphisa ukusabalala komkhuhlane, i-coronavirus, nezinye izifo ezithathelwanayo; ukuvimbela izimbangela ezithathelwanayo zohudo; ukunciphisa ukutheleleka kwezifo zokuphefumula;
kanye nokunciphisa izinga lokufa kwezinsana ekubelethweni ekhaya.
Ucwaningo lwango-2013 lwabonisa ukuthi izindlela zokugeza izandla ezithuthukisiwe zingaholela ekukhuleni okuncane kokukhula kobude ezinganeni ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu ubudala.
Emazweni asathuthuka, izinga lokufa kwezingane ezibangelwa izifo zokuphefumula nezifo zohudo lingancishiswa ngokwenza izinguquko ezilula zokuziphatha, njengokugeza izandla ngensipho.
Lesi senzo esilula singanciphisa izinga lokufa okubangelwa yilezi zifo cishe ngo-50%.
Ukungenelela okukhuthaza ukugeza izandla kunganciphisa izifo zohudo cishe ingxenye yesithathu, futhi lokhu kungafaniswa nokuhlinzeka ngamanzi ahlanzekile ezindaweni ezinemali ephansi.
Ukwehla kwezinga lokuqubuka kwamaphesenti angu-48 kungahlotshaniswa nokugeza izandla ngensipho. Ukugeza izandla ngensipho kuyindlela ephumelela kunazo zonke futhi engabizi kakhulu yokuvimbela ukuqubuka kanye nezifo zokuphefumula ezinzima (ARIs), njengoba kuyinto eyenzeka ngokuzenzakalelayo emakhaya, ezikoleni nasemphakathini emhlabeni wonke.
I-Pneumonia, i-ARI eyinhloko, iyimbangela eyinhloko yokufa kwezingane ezingaphansi kweminyaka emihlanu, ebulala izingane ezibalelwa ezigidini ezingu-1,8 ngonyaka.
Ukuvuvukala kwamaphaphu kanye ne - pneumonia ndawonye kubulala cishe izingane eziyizigidi ezingu - 3,5 unyaka ngamunye.
Ngokwe-UNICEF, ukugeza izandla ngensipho ngaphambi kokudla nangemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese kungasindisa izimpilo eziningi kunanoma yimuphi umuthi wokugoma noma wokwelapha, kunciphisa ukufa okubangelwa isifo sohudo cishe ngesigamu nokufa okubangelwa izifo ezinzima zokuphefumula ngengxenye eyodwa kwezine.
Ukugeza izandla kuvame ukuhlanganiswa nezinye izinhlelo zokuphepha njengengxenye yezinhlelo zokuphepha kwamanzi, ukuhlanzeka nokuhlanzeka (WASH).
Ukugeza izandla kuvikela futhi ekungenweni yi-impetigo, okudluliselwa ngokuthintana nomuntu ngqo.
Umphumela omncane omubi wokugeza izandla ukuthi ukugeza izandla njalo kungaholela ekulimaleni kwesikhumba ngenxa yokoma kwesikhumba.
Ucwaningo lwango-2012 lwaseDenmark lwathola ukuthi ukugeza izandla ngokweqile kungaholela esimweni sesikhumba esihlaba umxhwele, esibizwa ngokuthi i-eczema yesandla noma i-dermatitis yesandla, esivame kakhulu phakathi kwabasebenza kwezokwelapha.
Ukugeza izandla njalo kubhekwa njengesinye sezici zesifo sokucindezelwa nokuphoqeleka (OCD).
Kunezikhathi ezinhlanu ezibucayi phakathi nosuku lapho ukugeza izandla ngensipho kubalulekile khona ukunciphisa ukudluliselwa kwesifo nge-fecal-oral: ngemuva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese (ukuhlanza, ukuhlanza), ngemuva kokuhlanza ingane (ukushintsha amaphayiphu), ngaphambi kokondla ingane, ngaphambi kokudla nangaphambi / ngemuva kokulungiselela ukudla noma ukuphatha inyama eluhlaza, inhlanzi noma izinkukhu.
