Ukukhuthazwa nokukhuthazwa kokugeza izandla ngensipho kungathonya izinqumo zenqubomgomo, kwenze abantu bazi ngezinzuzo zokugeza izandla futhi kuholele ekuguqulweni kokuziphatha kwabantu isikhathi eside.
Ukuze lokhu kusebenze ngempumelelo, kudingeka ukuqapha nokuhlola.
Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile kwezifundo ezingu-70 kutholakale ukuthi izindlela ezisekelwe emphakathini ziyasebenza ekwandiseni ukugeza izandla kuma-LMICs, kuyilapho imikhankaso yokumaketha kwezenhlalo ingasebenzi kangako. Isibonelo sokukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ezikoleni "yi-Three Star Approach" ye-UNICEF ekhuthaza izikole ukuba zithathe izinyathelo ezilula, ezingabizi zokuqinisekisa ukuthi abafundi bayageza izandla zabo ngensipho, phakathi kwezinye izidingo zenhlanzeko.
Lapho izindinganiso eziphansi zifinyelelwa, izikole zingadlulela kusuka ezinkanyezini ezintathu ziye kwezintathu.
Ukwakha iziteshi zokugeza izandla kungaba yingxenye yemikhankaso yokukhuthaza ukugeza izandla eyenziwa ngenhloso yokunciphisa izifo nokufa kwezingane.
I-Global Handwashing Day ingenye isibonelo somkhankaso wokuqwashisa ozama ukufeza ushintsho ekuziphatheni. Ngenxa yobhubhane lwe-coronavirus lwango-2019-20, i-UNICEF yagqugquzela ukwamukelwa kwe-emoji yokuwasha izandla.
Zimbalwa izifundo ezibheke ukusebenza kwezindleko kokugeza izandla emazweni asathuthuka maqondana nama-DAYs avikelwe.
Kodwa-ke, ukubuyekeza okukodwa kusikisela ukuthi ukukhuthaza ukugeza izandla ngensipho kusebenza kakhulu ngokwezindleko kunamanye amasu okugeza amanzi nokukhucululwa kwendle.
"Ukubaluleka kokugeza izandla empilweni yabantu  ikakhulukazi kubantu abasebunzimeni njengabesifazane abasanda kubeletha noma amasosha alimele ezibhedlela  kwaqala kwaqashelwa maphakathi nekhulu le-19 ngamaphayona amabili okuhlanzeka kwezandla: udokotela waseHungary u-Ignaz Semmelweis owayesebenza eVienna, e-Austria noFlorence Nightingale, isiNgisi ""umsunguli wezokwelapha zanamuhla""".
Ngaleso sikhathi abantu abaningi babesakholelwa ukuthi izifo ezibangelwa amagciwane zazibangelwa iphunga elibi elibizwa ngokuthi ama-miasmas.
Ngawo-1980, ukuqubuka kwezifo ezibangelwa ukudla kanye nezifo ezihlobene nokunakekelwa kwezempilo kwaholela i-United States Centers for Disease Control and Prevention ukuba ikhuthaze ukuhlanzeka kwezandla njengendlela ebalulekile yokuvimbela ukusabalala kwesifo.
Ukuqubuka komkhuhlane wezingulube ngo-2009 kanye nobhubhane lwe-COVID-19 ngo-2020 kwaholela ekwandeni kokuqwashisa emazweni amaningi ngokubaluleka kokugeza izandla ngensipho ukuze uzivikele ezifweni ezinjalo ezithathelwanayo.
Ngokwesibonelo, kwakulengiswa amaposta "amasu okugeza izandla ngendlela efanele" eduze kosinki bezindlu zangasese zomphakathi nasemathayeleni ezakhiwo zamahhovisi nasezikhumulweni zezindiza eJalimane".
"Inkulumo ethi 'ukugeza izandla' ngokuthile, isho ukuthi umuntu akazimisele ukuzibophezela noma ukuba nesandla kulokho".
Livela esigabeni seBhayibheli kuMathewu lapho uPontiyu Pilatu ahlanza izandla zakhe esinqumweni sokubethelwa kukaJesu Kristu, kodwa sekuwumusho osetshenziswa kabanzi kweminye imiphakathi yamaNgisi.
Encwadini kaShakespeare ethi Macbeth, uNkosikazi Macbeth uqala ukugeza izandla zakhe ngokunganaki ezama ukuhlanza ibala eliyiphupho, okubonisa ukuthi unembeza wakhe uyamlahla ngecala lobugebengu ayebenze futhi wabangela umyeni wakhe ukuba enze.
Kuye kwatholakala nokuthi abantu, ngemva kokukhumbula noma ukucabanga ngezenzo ezingekho emthethweni, bathambekele ekugeza izandla kaningi kunabanye, futhi bathambekele ekuboniseni ukwazisa ngokwengeziwe ngezinto zokugeza izandla.
"Ngaphezu kwalokho, labo abavunyelwe ukugeza izandla zabo ngemva kokuthandaza ngale ndlela mancane amathuba okuba bahlanganyele kwezinye izenzo zokuziphindiselela, njengokuvolontiya".
Izinkolo zibeka ukugeza izandla ngezinhloso zokuhlanzeka nokwokufanekisa. Ukugeza izandla okungokomfanekiso, usebenzisa amanzi kodwa hhayi insipho ukugeza izandla, kuyingxenye yokuhlanza izandla okuyisiko ezinkolweni eziningi, kufaka phakathi i-Bahá'í Faith, ubuHindu, i-tevilah ne-netilat yadayim ebuJudeni, iLavobo ebuKrestwini, ne-Wudhu e-Islam. Izinkolo nazo zibeka ukugeza izandla ngendlela ehlanzekile, ikakhulukazi ngemuva kwemisebenzi ethile.
UbuHindu, ubuJuda nobuSulumani buyala ukuba umuntu ageze izandla ngemva kokusebenzisa indlu yangasese.
Futhi, ubuHindu, ubuBuddha, ubuSikh, ubuJuda nobuSulumane buyala ukugeza izandla ngaphambi nangemva kokudla.
Izindlela zokulawula izingozi ze-COVID-19 emsebenzini
Ukulawula izingozi emsebenzini ze-COVID-19 kuyindlela yokusebenzisa izindlela zokuphepha nezempilo emsebenzini zokulawula izingozi ekuvimbeleni isifo se-coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ukulawula izingozi okufanele emsebenzini kuncike endaweni yokusebenzela nasemsebenzini, ngokususelwa ekuhlolweni kwengozi yemithombo yokuchayeka, ubukhulu besifo emphakathini, kanye nezici zobungozi zabasebenzi ngabanye abangaba sengozini yokungenwa yi-COVID-19.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane bokuthi umuntu angagciniwe inobudlelwano obuncane nomphakathi kanye nabanye osebenza nabo, lapho kunconywa khona izindlela eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, okuhlanganisa ukugeza izandla, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, ukuziphatha ngendlela yokuphefumula, nokugcina inqubo yokuhlanza nokubulala amagciwane endaweni yokusebenza.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obumaphakathi ifaka phakathi leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma okuseduze nabantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ngokuba ne-COVID-19, kodwa abangase batheleleke ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo noma ukuhamba kwamanye amazwe.
Lokhu kuhlanganisa abasebenzi abanokuxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengezikole, izindawo zokusebenza ezinabantu abaningi, kanye nezinye izindawo ezinabantu abaningi.
Ukulawulwa kwengozi yaleli qembu, ngaphezu kwezindlela eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka, kuhlanganisa ukufaka umoya osebenza kahle ngokusebenzisa izihlungi zomoya, izivikelo zokuthimula, kanye nokuba nemishini yokuzivikela uma kwenzeka umuntu ehlangana ne-COVID-19.
I-OSHA ibheka izisebenzi zezempilo nezasemathuneni ezivezwe kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo ukuthi une-COVID-19 njengokungathi zisengozini enkulu yokuvezwa, okuphakamisa ingozi enkulu kakhulu yokuvezwa uma izisebenzi zenza izinqubo ezikhiqiza i-aerosol, noma ziqoqa noma ziphatha amasampula avela, kumuntu owaziwayo noma osolwayo one-COVID-19.
Izindlela zokulawula izingozi ezifanele lezi zisebenzi zihlanganisa izindlela zokulawula ezobunjiniyela ezifana nezindawo zokungenisa umoya ezinengcindezi engeyinhle, kanye nemishini yokuzivikela efanele umsebenzi.
Ukuqubuka kwe-COVID-19 kungaba nemiphumela eminingi emsebenzini.
Izisebenzi zingase zingabi khona emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula, isidingo sokunakekela abanye, noma ukwesaba ukuvezwa ingozi.
Amaphethini okuhweba angase ashintshe, kokubili ngokwempahla efunwayo, nezindlela zokuthola le mpahla (njengokuthenga ngezikhathi ezingaphansi kwezikhathi eziphakeme noma ngokulethwa noma ngezinsizakalo zokuhamba ngemoto).
Okokugcina, ukuthunyelwa kwezinto ezivela ezindaweni ezithinteke kakhulu yi-COVID-19 kungaphazanyiswa.Uhlelo lokulungela nokusabela kwezifo ezithathelwanayo lungasetshenziswa ukuqondisa izenzo zokuvikela.
Lezi zinhlelo zibheka amazinga obucayi ahambisana nezindawo zokusebenza nemisebenzi ehlukahlukene, kuhlanganise imithombo yokuchayeka, izingozi ezivela ekhaya nasemphakathini, nezingozi ezenzeka kubasebenzi ngabanye njengokuguga noma izimo zempilo ezingapheli.
Ziphinde zichaze izindlela zokulawula ezidingekayo ukuze kubhekwane nalezi zingozi, kanye nezinhlelo zokuzivikela ezimweni ezingase zivele ngenxa yokuqubuka kwalezi zifo.
Izinhlelo zokuqapha izifo ezithathelwanayo nezokulwa nazo zingase zibe ngaphansi kwezincomo zikazwelonke noma ezingaphansi kukazwelonke.
Izinhloso zokuphendula ekuqubukeni zihlanganisa ukunciphisa ukudluliswa phakathi kwabasebenzi, ukuvikela abantu abasengozini enkulu yokuthinteka kwezempilo, ukugcina imisebenzi yebhizinisi, nokunciphisa imiphumela emibi kwezinye izinhlangano ezisezinhlinzekweni zabo.
Ubukhulu besifo emphakathini lapho ibhizinisi litholakala khona kuthinta izimpendulo ezithathwe.
I-hierarchy of hazard controls iyindlela esetshenziswa kakhulu kwezokuphepha kanye nempilo emsebenzini ukuhlukanisa ukulawulwa kwengozi ngokusebenza.
Lapho izingozi ze-COVID-19 zingenakuqedwa khona, izindlela zokulawula ezisebenza kangcono kakhulu ezokwakha, zilandelwa izindlela zokuphatha, bese kuba imishini yokuzivikela.
Ukulawulwa kwezobunjiniyela kuhilela ukuhlukanisa abasebenzi ezingozini ezihlobene nomsebenzi ngaphandle kokuthembela ekuziphatheni kwesisebenzi, futhi kungaba yisixazululo esibiza kakhulu sokusebenzisa.
Ukulawula okuphathekayo yizinguquko zenqubomgomo noma izinqubo zomsebenzi ezidinga isenzo somsebenzi noma somqashi.
Imishini yokuzivikela (PPE) ibhekwa njengengasebenzi kangako kunezindlela zokulawula ezobunjiniyela nezokuphatha, kodwa ingasiza ekuvimbeleni ukuchayeka okuthile.
Zonke izinhlobo ze-PPE kufanele zikhethwe ngokususelwa engozini ezisebenzini, zifakwe kahle uma zikhona (isib. izivikelo zokuphefumula), zigqokwe njalo futhi ngendlela efanele, zihlolwe njalo, zigcinwe, futhi zishintshwe, uma kunesidingo, futhi zisuswe, zihlanzwe, zigcinwe noma zilahlwe ngendlela efanele ukuze kugwenywe ukungcola.
Ngokwe-U.S. Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA), imisebenzi enobungozi obuncane kakhulu yokungcoliswa, ihlanganisa ukuhlangana okuncane kakhulu nomphakathi kanye nabanye osebenza nabo.
Izinyathelo eziyisisekelo zokuvimbela ukutheleleka ezinconyelwayo kuzo zonke izindawo zokusebenza zihlanganisa ukugeza izandla njalo futhi kahle, ukukhuthaza abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya uma begula, ukuziphatha okuphathelene nokuphefumula okuhlanganisa ukuvala ukukhwehlela nokuthimula, ukuhlinzeka ngezicubu kanye nezindawo zokulahla udoti, ukulungiselela ukusebenza ngocingo noma ukushintshana uma kunesidingo, ukuvimbela abasebenzi ekusebenziseni amathuluzi nemishini yabanye, nokugcina ukuhlanzwa nokubulala amagciwane okujwayelekile endaweni yokusebenza.
Ukuhlonza ngokushesha nokuhlukanisa abantu abangase batheleleke kuyisinyathelo esibalulekile ekuvikeleni abasebenzi, amakhasimende, izivakashi nabanye endaweni yokusebenza.
I-U.S. Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) incoma ukuthi abasebenzi abanezimpawu zesifo sokuphefumula esibucayi kufanele bahlale ekhaya kuze kube yilapho bengasenayo imfiva, izimpawu zemfiva, nanoma yiziphi ezinye izimpawu okungenani amahora angu-24 ngaphandle kokusebenzisa imithi yokunciphisa imfiva noma eminye imithi eguqula izimpawu, nokuthi izinqubomgomo zokungayi emsebenzini ngenxa yokugula ziyaguquguquka, zivumela abasebenzi ukuba bahlale ekhaya ukuze banakekele ilungu lomndeni eligulayo, nokuthi abasebenzi bayazi lezi zinqubomgomo.
Ngokwe-OSHA, imisebenzi enobungozi obuphakathi ifaka phakathi leyo edinga ukuxhumana njalo noma okuseduze nabantu abangekho ngaphansi kwamamitha ayisithupha (1.8 m) abantu abangaziwa noma abasolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19, kodwa abangase babe ne-SARS-CoV-2 ngenxa yokudluliselwa komphakathi okuqhubekayo endaweni yebhizinisi, noma ngoba umuntu usanda kuhambela kwamanye amazwe endaweni enokudluliswa kwe-COVID-19 okwandile.
Lezi zihlanganisa abasebenzi abaxhumana nomphakathi jikelele njengezikolo, izindawo zokusebenza ezinabantu abaningi, kanye nezindawo ezinabantu abaningi. Ukulawulwa kobunjiniyela kwala maqembu anobungozi obukhulu kubandakanya ukufakwa kwezihlungi zomoya ezisebenza kahle kakhulu, ukukhuphula amazinga okuphephula umoya, ukufaka izithiyo ezibonakalayo ezifana nezihlungi zepulasitiki ezicacile, nokufaka iwindi lokuhamba ukuze kusetshenziswe amakhasimende. Ukulawulwa kokuphatha kwalawa maqembu anobungozi obukhulu kubandakanya ukukhuthaza abasebenzi abagulayo ukuba bahlale ekhaya, esikhundleni semihlangano yabantu ubuso nobuso ngezokuxhumana, ukusungula amashifu ahlukanisiwe, ukuyeka ukuhamba okungabalulekile ezindaweni lapho kuqhubeka khona izifo ze-COVID-19, ukuthuthukisa izinhlelo zokuxhumana ezibandakanya iforamu yokuphendula ukukhathazeka kwabasebenzi, ukuhlinzeka ngemfundo esesikhathini nokuqeqeshwa mayelana nezingozi ze-COVID-19 kanye nokuziphatha okuvikelekile, ukuqeqesha abasebenzi abadinga ukusebenzisa amagilavu namathuluzi okuvikelayo, ukuhlinzeka ngemithombo yokuvikela nokuhlinzeka indawo edinga ukuhlanzeka ngokusobala, nokufaka amafasitela okuhlanzekile okudlayo, ukugeza izandla nokuzipha, ukuhambisa izisebenzi zokuzivikela ubuso, noma ezinye izindlela zokuzivikela abasebenzi ababhekana nobuso, ukugeza izandla, ukugeza izandla, noma ukugeza izandla, noma ukugeza izandla, ukugeza izandla, noma ukugeza izisebenzi, noma ukugeza izandla noma ukufinyelela okuvikela okujwayelekile, kanye neminye izindlela zokuzi, ukubhekana nokweqabula kwamakhasimende.
Abasebenzi abakuleli qembu elisengozini badinga ukusetshenziswa kweziphephetha.
Uma umuntu egula endizeni, izindlela ezifanele zokuvikela abasebenzi nabanye abagibeli zihlanganisa ukuhlukanisa umuntu ogulayo kwabanye ngesivinini esingamamitha amabili, ukukhetha ilungu elilodwa labasebenzi ukuba lisebenze nomuntu ogulayo, nokunikeza umuntu ogulayo imaski yobuso noma ukucela umuntu ogulayo ukuba amboze umlomo nekhala ngamashizi lapho ekhwehlela noma ethimula.
Abasebenzi basemagumbini kufanele bagqoke amagilavu okuzivikela alahlwa kanye uma benakekela umuntu ogulayo ohambayo noma bethinta uketshezi lomzimba noma izindawo ezingase zingcoliswe, futhi mhlawumbe bagqoke nezinye izinto zokuzivikela uma umuntu ogulayo enomkhuhlane, ukukhwehlela okungapheli, noma enenkinga yokuphefumula.
Amagilavu nezinye izinto ezilahlwayo kufanele zilahlwe esikhwameni se-biodependent, futhi izindawo ezingcolile kufanele zihlanzwe futhi zihlatshwe amagciwane ngemuva kwalokho. Kwezokuthutha ngezimpahla, okubandakanya imikhumbi yokuhamba ngomkhumbi nezinye imikhumbi zabagibeli, ukulawula ubungozi kufaka phakathi ukubambezela uhambo uma umuntu egula, nokuzihlukanisa nokuxhumana nesikhungo sezokwelapha esikhungweni ngokushesha uma umuntu eba nomkhuhlane noma ezinye izimpawu ngenkathi esemkhunjini.
Ngokufanelekile, ukuqapha kwezokwelapha kufanele kwenzeke endaweni yomuntu ohlukanisiwe. Ezikoleni nasezikhungweni zokunakekela izingane, i-CDC incoma ukuvalwa kwesikhashana ukuze kuhlanzwe noma kubulawe amagciwane uma umuntu onegciwane esekade esakhiweni sesikole kungakhathalekile ukuthi usakazeke emphakathini.
Lapho kunokusakazeka okuncane noma okulingene komphakathi, amasu okuhlukanisa abantu komunye nomunye angenziwa njengokukhansela uhambo lwasensimini, imihlangano, neminye imibuthano emikhulu efana nemfundo yokuzivocavoca noma amakilasi e-choir noma ukudla endaweni yokudlela, ukwandisa isikhala phakathi kwamadeski, izikhathi ezifika nezokuphuma eziphazamisayo, ukunciphisa izivakashi ezingadingekile, nokusebenzisa indawo ehlukile yehhovisi lezempilo yezingane ezinezimpawu ezifana nomkhuhlane.
Lapho kunokusakazeka okukhulu emphakathini wendawo, ngaphezu kwamasu okuhlukanisa abantu, kungacatshangelwa ukuxoshwa kwezingane isikhathi eside esikoleni. Kwabasebenzi bezomthetho abenza imisebenzi yansuku zonke, i-CDC ibheka ingozi yezempilo esheshayo njengencane.
Izikhulu eziphoqelela umthetho okumele zithintane nabantu okuqinisekiswe noma okusolwa ukuthi bane-COVID-19 zinconywa ukuba zilandele iziqondiso ezifanayo nezisebenzi zezokwelapha eziphuthumayo, kuhlanganise nemishini efanele yokuzivikela.
Uma kwenzeka ukuhlangana eduze ngesikhathi kubanjwa, abasebenzi kufanele bahlanze futhi babulale amagciwane amabhande abo kanye nemishini ngaphambi kokuba baphinde bayisebenzise besebenzisa umuthi wokuhlanza indlu noma isula, futhi balandele izinqubo ezijwayelekile zokusebenza zokufakwa nokulahlwa kwe-PPE esetshenzisiwe kanye nokugcina nokuhlanza izingubo.
I-OSHA ibheka izisebenzi ezithile zezempilo nezingcwaba njengezikweletwa kakhulu noma ezisezingeni eliphezulu kakhulu.
Imisebenzi enobungozi obukhulu ifaka ukulethwa kwezempilo, ukusekela, abasebenzi basemalabhorethri, kanye nabasebenza kwezokuhamba kwezokwelapha abachayeke ezigulini ezaziwayo noma ezisolwayo ze-COVID-19.
Lezi ziba nengozi enkulu kakhulu yokuchayeka uma abasebenzi benza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, noma beqoqa noma bephatha amasampula ezigulane ze-COVID-19 ezaziwayo noma ezisolisayo.
Izinqubo ezikhiqiza i-aerosol zihlanganisa ukufaka i-intubation, izinqubo zokukhwehlela, i-bronchoscopy, ezinye izinqubo zokuhlolwa kwamazinyo, noma ukuqoqwa kwesampula.
Imisebenzi yokuhlonza izidumbu enobungozi obukhulu ifaka phakathi izisebenzi ezibandakanyeka ekulungiseleleni izidumbu zabantu ababenamacala awaziwayo noma asolisayo e-COVID-19 ngesikhathi sokufa kwabo; lokhu kuba ingozi enkulu kakhulu yokuvezwa uma benza ukuhlonza.Izilawuli ezingeziwe zobunjiniyela zalawa maqembu anobungozi zifaka amakamelo okuhlukaniswa eziguli ezinamacala awaziwayo noma asolisayo e-COVID-19, kuhlanganise nalapho kwenziwa izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol.
Ukuphefumula okuhlonyisiwe okungasebenzi kahle kungase kufaneleke kwezinye izindawo zokunakekela impilo nasezindaweni zokungcwaba.
Izibonelo kufanele ziphathwe ngokuqapha kweBiosafety Level 3.
Inhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba (i-WHO) incoma ukuthi iziguli ezifikayo zihlukaniswe ezindaweni zokulinda ezihlukile kuye ngokuthi zisola ukuthi zine-COVID-19 yini. Ngaphezu kwezinye izinto zokuvikela ezomuntu siqu, i-OSHA incoma ukuthi labo abasebenza endaweni engamamitha angu-6 ukusuka ezigulini ezaziwa ukuthi zine-SARS-CoV-2, noma kusolwa ukuthi zine-SARS-CoV-2, nalabo abenza izinqubo zokukhiqiza i-aerosol, kufanele babe neziphefumulo.
E-United States, ama-N95 avunyelwe yi-NIOSH ukuhlunga ama-facepiece respirators noma okungcono kumele kusetshenziswe esimweni sohlelo oluphelele, olubhaliwe lokuvikela ukuphefumula olufaka ukuhlolwa kokufaneleka, ukuqeqeshwa, nokuhlolwa kwezokwelapha.
Ezinye izinhlobo ze-respirator zingahlinzeka ngokuvikeleka okukhulu futhi zithuthukise induduzo yabasebenzi. I-WHO ayikhuthazi ama-coveralls, njengoba i-COVID-19 iyisifo sokuphefumula kunokuba idluliselwe ngemithambo yomzimba.
I-WHO incoma ukuthi abasebenzi abahlola abantu abavela kwamanye amazwe bafanele bafake izifihla-buso kuphela.
Kulabo abaqoqa amasampula okuphefumula, abanakekela, noma abathutha iziguli ezine-COVID-19 ngaphandle kwezinqubo ezikhiqiza i-aerosol, i-WHO incoma imaski yokuhlinza, izibuko zokuzivikela, noma isihlangu sobuso, ingubo, namagilavu.
Uma kwenziwa inqubo yokukhiqiza i-aerosol, imaski yokuhlinzwa ingashintshwa nge-N95 noma i-FFP2 yokuphefumula.
