I-Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) iyinhlanganisela ye-enzyme enamathiselwe ebusweni obungaphandle (izindwangu zamaseli) zamaseli emaphashini, emithanjeni, enhliziyweni, ezinso nasesiswini.
I-ACE2 ivimbela umsebenzi we-enzyme ehlobene ne-angiotensin-converting (ACE) ngokunciphisa inani le-angiotensin-II nokwandisa i-Ang ((1-7) okwenza kube umgomo wezidakamizwa othembisayo wokwelapha izifo zenhliziyo nemithambo yegazi. I-ACE2 futhi isebenza njengendawo yokungena emangqamuzaneni kwamanye ama-coronavirus.
Inguqulo yabantu ye-enzyme ivame ukubizwa ngokuthi yi- hACE2.
I- angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 iyinhlanganisela ye- zinc equkethe i- metalloenzyme etholakala ebusweni be- endothelial namanye amaseli.
I- ACE2 protein iqukethe i- N- terminal peptidase M2 domain kanye ne- C- terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
I-ACE2 iyi-membrane protein enohlobo I oludlula kanye, enendawo yayo esebenzayo ye-enzymatic evezwe ebusweni bamangqamuzana emaphashini nakwezinye izicubu.
Isizinda esingaphandle kwamangqamuzana se - ACE2 sihlukaniswa nesizinda se - transmembrane ngenye i - enzyme eyaziwa ngokuthi i - sheddase, futhi i - protein encibilikayo ephumayo ikhishwa egazini futhi ekugcineni ikhishwe emchameni.
I-ACE2 ikhona ezinhlizini eziningi: I-ACE2 inamathele kulwelwelwesi lwama-alveolar cells ikakhulukazi ohlobo II lwamaphaphu, ama-enterocytes emathumbu amancane, amangqamuzana e-endothelial ezinzwa kanye nemithambo kanye namangqamuzana omzimba omzimba omnene emithambo eminingi.
Ukubonakaliswa kwe-mRNA ye-ACE2 kutholakala futhi ku-cerebral cortex, striatum, hypothalamus, nasegxeni lobuchopho.
Umsebenzi oyinhloko we - ACE2 ukuba abe isilinganiso esiphikisayo se - ACE.
I-ACE ihlukanisa i-angiotensin I ihlukanise i-angiotensin II ecindezela imithambo yegazi.
I- carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine ihlukaniswa nge-angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) bese i-hydrolyses ibe yi-angiotensin (1- 7), (H ACE-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
I-ACE2 ingahlukanisa namanye ama-peptide amaningi kuhlanganise ne- [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, i-apelin, i-neurotensin, i-dynorphin A, ne-ghrelin.
I-ACE2 ilawula nokuthuthwa kwe-membrane kwe-neutral amino acid transporter SLC6A19 futhi ibandakanyekile esifweni sikaHartnup.
Njengeprotheni ye-transmembrane, i-ACE2 isebenza njengendawo yokungena eyinhloko kumaseli amanye ama-coronavirus, kufaka phakathi i-HCoV-NL63; i-SARS-CoV (igciwane elibangela i-SARS); kanye ne-SARS-CoV-2 (igciwane elibangela i-COVID-19).
Ngokuqondile, ukubopha kwe-spike S1 protein ye-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV2 ku-enzyme domain ye-ACE2 ebusweni bamaseli kuholela ku-endocytosis kanye nokudluliselwa kokubili kwegciwane kanye ne-enzyme kuma-endosomes atholakala ngaphakathi kwamaseli.
Le nqubo yokungena futhi idinga ukuqala kweprotheni ye-S yi-serine protease TMPRSS2 yomgcini, okuvinjelwa kwayo okwamanje kuphenywa njengokwelapha okungenzeka. Lokhu kuholele abanye ukuba bacabange ukuthi ukwehlisa amazinga e-ACE2, kumaseli, kungasiza ekulweni nokutheleleka.
Nokho, izinhlangano eziningi zezokwelapha nemibutho elawulayo ziye zeluleka ukuba kuqhutshekwe ukwelashwa okuvamile kwe-ACE inhibitor ne-ARB.
"Ukubuyekezwa okuhlelekile kanye nokuhlaziywa kwe-meta okushicilelwe ngoJulayi 11, 2012, kutholakale ukuthi "" ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors kwakuhlotshaniswa nokunciphisa okuphawulekayo okungu-34% kwengozi yesifo samaphaphu uma kuqhathaniswa nokulawula. """
" Ngaphezu kwalokho, "" ingozi yesifo samaphaphu nayo yehliswa ezigulini eziphathwe nge- ACE inhibitors ezazisengozini enkulu yokuphathwa yisifo samaphaphu, ikakhulukazi lezo ezazinesifo sohlangothi nokuhluleka kwenhliziyo. "
" Ukusetshenziswa kwama-ACE inhibitors nakho kwahlotshaniswa nokwehliswa kokufa okuhlobene ne-pneumonia, nakuba imiphumela yayingaqiniseki kangako kunengozi ephelele ye-pneumonia. """
I-ACE2 yabantu ehlanganisiwe (rhACE2) kucatshangwa ukuthi iyindlela yokwelapha entsha yokulimala kwamaphaphu okubukhali, futhi ibonakala ithuthukisa i-hemodynamics yamaphaphu nokugcwala komoya ezingulubeni ezinesifo sokuphefumula esibangelwa i-lipopolysaccharide.
I- rhACE2 i- half- life kubantu cishe amahora angu- 10 futhi i- onset of action imizuzu engu- 30 ngaphezu kwe- course of effect (isikhathi) yamahora angu- 24.
Imiphumela eminingi ibonisa ukuthi i-rHACE2 ingaba umuthi othembisayo kulabo abangakwazi ukubekezelela ama-renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (ama-RAS inhibitors) noma ezifweni lapho i-angiotensin II esezingeni eliphezulu. I-rHACE2 efakwe ngaphakathi iye yahlolwa ezivivinyweni zomtholampilo zokwelapha i-acute respiratory distress syndrome.
