NgoJanuwari 2020, i-WHO yancoma i-2019-nCov kanye ne-2019-nCoV acute respiratory disease njengamagama esikhashana egciwane nesifo ngokuhambisana nesiqondiso sika-2015 sokungazisebenzisi izindawo ngamagama ezifo kanye namagciwane.
Amagama asemthethweni i-COVID-19 ne-SARS-CoV-2 akhishwa ngo-11 February 2020.
Ngenxa yokulinganiselwa kwamandla emishini ejwayelekile, abanye abakhiqizi bezinto ezidijithali bakhiqiza izinto zokunakekelwa kwezempilo ezifana nama-nasal swabs nezingxenye ze-ventilator.
Kwesinye isibonelo, lapho isibhedlela sase-Italy sidinga ngokushesha i-valve yokufakelwa umoya, futhi umphakeli engakwazi ukuletha ngesikhathi esibekiwe, inkampani yasendaweni yasungula futhi yanyathelisa ama-valve ayikhulu ayedingeka ngobusuku obubodwa.
Ngemuva kokuqubuka kokuqala kwe-COVID-19, kwavela imibono yokuqamba amanga, ukwaziswa okungelona iqiniso nokungaziwa mayelana nemvelaphi, izinga, ukuvimbela, ukwelashwa nezinye izici zesifo futhi zasakazeka ngokushesha ku-inthanethi.
Kubonakala sengathi abantu bayakwazi ukusakaza igciwane kwezinye izilwane.
Lolu cwaningo aluzange lukwazi ukuthola ubufakazi bokuthi igciwane liyaphindaphindeka ezingulubeni, emadada nasezinkukhu.
Ayikho imithi noma umuthi wokugoma ovunyiwe wokwelapha lesi sifo.
Ucwaningo lwamazwe ngamazwe ngemigomo nemithi ye-COVID-19 luyaqhubeka nezinhlangano zikahulumeni, amaqembu ezemfundo kanye nabacwaningi bemboni.
"NgoMashi, iNhlangano Yezempilo Yomhlaba wonke yaqala i-"SOLIDARITY Trial"" ukuhlola imiphumela yokwelashwa kwezidakamizwa ezine ezikhona eziphikisana namagciwane ezinethemba elikhulu lokusebenza".
Asikho isibhamu esitholakalayo, kodwa izinhlangano ezihlukahlukene zisebenza ngenkuthalo ekuthuthukiseni izibhamu.
Umsebenzi wangaphambilini we-SARS-CoV usetshenziswa ngoba i-SARS-CoV ne-SARS-CoV-2 zombili zisebenzisa i-ACE2 receptor ukungena kumaseli omuntu.
Kunezindlela ezintathu zokugoma ezicwaningwayo.
Okokuqala, abacwaningi bahlela ukwakha umuthi wokugoma ogcwele igciwane.
Ukusetshenziswa kwaleli gciwane, kungakhathaliseki ukuthi alisebenzi noma lifile, kuhloswe ngalo ukuvusa ukusabela komzimba okusheshayo komzimba womuntu ekungenweni okusha kwe-COVID-19.
Indlela yesibili, imithi yokugoma yezingxenye ezithile, ihlose ukudala umuthi wokugoma owenza isimiso sokuzivikela sizwele ezingxenyeni ezithile zegciwane.
Endabeni ye-SARS-CoV-2, ucwaningo olunjalo lugxile ku-S-spike protein esiza igciwane lingene ku-ACE2 enzyme receptor.
Isu lesithathu liwukuthi imithi yokugoma ye - nucleic acid (imithi yokugoma ye - DNA noma i - RNA, indlela entsha yokwakha umuthi wokugoma).
Imigomo yokuhlola evela kunoma yiliphi lamasu kufanele ihlolwe ukuphepha nokusebenza kwayo. Ngo-16 Mashi 2020, ukuhlolwa kokuqala kwemitholampilo komuthi wokugoma kwaqala ngamavolontiya amane eSeattle.
Umuthi wokugoma uqukethe i-genetic code engenabungozi ekopishwe egciwane elibangela lesi sifo. Ukuthuthukiswa okuxhomeke kuma-antibody kuye kwasikiselwa njengenkinga engaba khona ekuthuthukisweni komuthi wokugoma we-SARS-COV-2, kodwa lokhu kuyimpikiswano.
Kunezivivinyo zemitholampilo ezingaphezu kuka-300 eziqhubekayo kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020.
Kwakunezivivinyo eziyisikhombisa ezazihlola izindlela zokwelapha umalaleveva esezivunyiwe kakade, kuhlanganise nezifundo ezine ze- hydroxychloroquine noma i-chloroquine.
Imithi elwa namagciwane e-repurposed ihlanganisa iningi locwaningo lwaseChina, kanti izivivinyo eziyisishiyagalolunye zesigaba III ze-remdesivir emazweni amaningi kufanele zibike ekupheleni kuka-Ephreli.
Ukubuyekezwa okunamandla kokuthuthukiswa kwemithi yokugoma ye-COVID-19 kanye nemithi yokugoma kwakukhona, kusukela ngo-Ephreli 2020. Imithi eminingi ekhona elwa namagciwane iyahlolwa ukuze kusetshenziswe ukwelashwa kwe-COVID-19, okuhlanganisa i-remdesivir, i-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine, i-lopinavir/ritonavir ne-lopinavir/ritonavir ihlanganiswe ne-interferon beta.
Kukhona ubufakazi obuncane bokusebenza kwe-remdesivir, kusukela ngoMashi 2020.
Ukuphuculwa komtholampilo kwabonwa ezigulini ezilashwa nge-remdesivir yokusebenzisa isihawu.
Izivivinyo zokwelashwa ze-Phase III zenziwa e-US, e-China nase-Italy. I-Chloroquine, eyayisetshenziselwa ukwelapha umalaleveva, yafundwa e-China ngoFebhuwari 2020, kwaba nemiphumela yokuqala.
Nokho, kunezidingo zokubuyekezwa kwalolu cwaningo.
Iziphathimandla Zempilo zaseKorea naseChina zikhuthaza ukusetshenziswa kwe-chloroquine.
Nokho, i-Wuhan Institute of Virology, nakuba incoma umthamo wansuku zonke ongu-gram eyodwa, iphawula ukuthi ukuphindeka kabili kwalowo mgomo kuyingozi kakhulu futhi kungabulala.
Ngo-28 Mashi 2020, i-FDA yakhipha imvume yokusetshenziswa okuphuthumayo kwe-hydroxychloroquine ne-chloroquine ngokubona kodokotela abalapha abantu abane-COVID-19.Iziqondiso zenguqulo yesi-7 zaseChina zifaka ne-interferon, i-ribavirin noma i-umifenovir ukuze zisetshenziswe ngokumelene ne-COVID-19.
Imininingwane yokuqala ibonisa ukuthi kudingeka imithamo emikhulu ye-ribavirin ukuze kuvinjwe i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
I-Nitazoxanide iye yanconywa ukuthi isetshenziswe ekucwaningeni okungeziwe kwe-in vivo ngemva kokubonisa ukuvimbela okuphansi kwe-SARS-CoV-2. Ucwaningo luye lwabonisa ukuthi ukuqala kokugxila kwe-spike protein yi-transmembrane protease serine 2 (TMPRSS2) kubalulekile ukuze i-SARS-CoV-2 ingene ngokusebenzisa ukusebenzisana ne-ACE2 receptor.
Ucwaningo lwe-chloroquine ne-hydroxychloroquine nge-azithromycin noma ngaphandle kwayo lunemikhawulo emikhulu evimbele umphakathi wezokwelapha ekwamukeleni lemithi yokwelapha ngaphandle kokuqhubeka nokucwaninga. I-Oseltamivir ayivimbeli i-SARS-CoV-2 in vitro futhi ayinayo indima eyaziwayo ekwelapheni i-COVID-19.
Isiphepho se-cytokine singaba inkinga ezinyathelweni zokugcina ze-COVID-19 enzima.
Kunobufakazi bokuthi i-hydroxychloroquine ingaba nemikhiqizo elwa nesiphepho se-cytokine. I-Tocilizumab ifakiwe eziqondisweni zokwelashwa yi-National Health Commission yaseChina ngemuva kokuphothulwa kocwaningo oluncane.
Lesi sidakamizwa sesigaba sesibili sesivivinywa ezingeni likazwelonke e-Italy ngemuva kokuthola imiphumela emihle kubantu abanesifo esibi.
Kuhlanganiswe nokuhlolwa kwegazi kwe-serum ferritin ukuze kutholakale iziphepho ze-cytokine, kuhloswe ukuba kuphikiswane nalezi zenzakalo, okucatshangwa ukuthi ziyimbangela yokufa kwabanye abantu abathintekayo.
I-interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yavunywa yi-FDA ngokusekelwe ezifundweni zecala ezibuyayo zokwelapha i-steroid refractory cytokine release syndrome ebangelwe yimbangela ehlukile, ukwelashwa kwe-CAR T cell, ngo-2017.
Kuze kube manje, abukho ubufakazi obuhleliwe, obulawulwayo bokuthi i- tocilizumab iyindlela ephumelelayo yokwelapha i- CRS.
Ukudlulisa ama-antibody ahlanzekile futhi agxilile akhiqizwa amasosha omzimba alabo asebephulukiswe ku-COVID-19 kubantu abawadingayo kuphenywa njengendlela yokugoma engeyona eyokugoma.
Leli qhinga lalinganelwa i-SARS kodwa imiphumela yayingaba eqinisekile.
Ukwehliswa kwegciwane kuyindlela okulindeleke ukuthi isebenze ngayo lapho ukwelashwa kwamagciwane okungahleliwe kungenza ukuvikela ngokumelene ne-SARS-CoV-2.
Kodwa-ke, ezinye izindlela, njenge-cytotoxicity cell cell ethembele ku-antibody kanye/noma i-phagocytosis, kungenzeka.
Ezinye izindlela zokwelapha ngama-antibody, ngokwesibonelo, ngokusebenzisa ama-antibody e-monoclonal akhiqizwayo, zisathuthukiswa.
Ukukhiqizwa kwe-serum yokululama, okuyingxenye engamanzi yegazi leziguli ezilungisiwe futhi equkethe ama-antibody akhethekile kuleligciwane, kungandiswa ukuze kusetshenziswe ngokushesha.
